var book = {
	"name": "Acts",
	"numChapters": 28,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>In the first book, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26913A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26913A\"></sup>Theophilus, I have dealt with all that Jesus began <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26913B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26913B\"></sup>to do and teach,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>until the day when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26914C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26914C\"></sup>he was taken up, after he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26914D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26914D\"></sup>had given commands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26914E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26914E\"></sup>through the Holy Spirit to the apostles whom he had chosen.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26915F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26915F\"></sup>He presented himself alive to them after his suffering by many proofs, appearing to them during forty days and speaking about the kingdom of God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And while staying with them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26916G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26916G\"></sup>he ordered them not to depart from Jerusalem, but to wait for the promise of the Father, which, he said, <span class=\"woj\">“you heard from me;</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26917H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26917H\"></sup>John baptized with water, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26917I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26917I\"></sup>but you will be baptized <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26917J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26917J\"></sup>with the Holy Spirit not many days from now.”</span>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So when they had come together, they asked him, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26918K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26918K\"></sup>will you at this time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26918L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26918L\"></sup>restore the kingdom to Israel?”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He said to them, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26919M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26919M\"></sup>“It is not for you to know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26919N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26919N\"></sup>times or seasons that the Father has fixed by his own authority.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But you will receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26920O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26920O\"></sup>power <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26920P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26920P\"></sup>when the Holy Spirit has come upon you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26920Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26920Q\"></sup>you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26920R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26920R\"></sup>my witnesses in Jerusalem and in all Judea and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26920S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26920S\"></sup>Samaria, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26920T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26920T\"></sup>to the end of the earth.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And when he had said these things, as they were looking on, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26921U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26921U\"></sup>he was lifted up, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26921V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26921V\"></sup>a cloud took him out of their sight.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And while they were gazing into heaven as he went, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26922W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26922W\"></sup>two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26922X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26922X\"></sup>men stood by them in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26922Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26922Y\"></sup>white robes,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26923Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26923Z\"></sup>“Men of Galilee, why do you stand looking into heaven? This Jesus, who was taken up from you into heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26923AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26923AA\"></sup>will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26923AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26923AB\"></sup>come in the same way as you saw him go into heaven.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26924AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26924AC\"></sup>they returned to Jerusalem from the mount called Olivet, which is near Jerusalem, a Sabbath day's journey away.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And when they had entered, they went up to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26925AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26925AD\"></sup>the upper room, where they were staying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26925AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26925AE\"></sup>Peter and John and James and Andrew, Philip and Thomas, Bartholomew and Matthew, James the son of Alphaeus and Simon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26925AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26925AF\"></sup>the Zealot and Judas the son of James.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>All these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26926AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26926AG\"></sup>with one accord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26926AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26926AH\"></sup>were devoting themselves to prayer, together with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26926AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26926AI\"></sup>the women and Mary the mother of Jesus, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26926AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26926AJ\"></sup>his brothers.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>In those days Peter stood up among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26927AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26927AK\"></sup>the brothers (the company of persons was in all about 120) and said,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26928AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26928AL\"></sup>the Scripture had to be fulfilled, which the Holy Spirit spoke beforehand by the mouth of David concerning Judas, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26928AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26928AM\"></sup>who became a guide to those who arrested Jesus.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26929AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26929AN\"></sup>he was numbered among us and was allotted his share in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26929AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26929AO\"></sup>this ministry.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>(Now this man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26930AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26930AP\"></sup>acquired a field with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26930AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26930AQ\"></sup>the reward of his wickedness, and falling headlong he burst open in the middle and all his bowels gushed out.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And it became known to all the inhabitants of Jerusalem, so that the field was called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26931AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26931AR\"></sup>in their own language Akeldama, that is, Field of Blood.)",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“For it is written in the Book of Psalms,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26932AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26932AS\"></sup>“‘May his camp become desolate,and let there be no one to dwell in it’;and<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26932AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26932AT\"></sup>“‘Let another take his office.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So one of the men who have accompanied us during <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26933AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26933AU\"></sup>all the time that the Lord Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26933AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26933AV\"></sup>went in and out among us,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26934AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26934AW\"></sup>beginning from the baptism of John until the day when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26934AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26934AX\"></sup>he was taken up from us—one of these men must become with us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26934AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26934AY\"></sup>a witness to his resurrection.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And they put forward two, Joseph called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26935AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26935AZ\"></sup>Barsabbas, who was also called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26935BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26935BA\"></sup>Justus, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26935BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26935BB\"></sup>Matthias.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26936BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26936BC\"></sup>they prayed and said, “You, Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26936BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26936BD\"></sup>who know the hearts of all, show which one of these two you have chosen",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>to take the place in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26937BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26937BE\"></sup>this ministry and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26937BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26937BF\"></sup>apostleship from which Judas turned aside to go to his own place.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And they cast lots for them, and the lot fell on Matthias, and he was numbered with the eleven apostles."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26939A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26939A\"></sup>the day of Pentecost arrived, they were all together in one place.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And suddenly there came from heaven a sound like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26940B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26940B\"></sup>a mighty rushing wind, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26940C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26940C\"></sup>it filled the entire house where they were sitting.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And divided tongues <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26941D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26941D\"></sup>as of fire appeared to them and rested on each one of them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And they were all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26942E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26942E\"></sup>filled with the Holy Spirit and began <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26942F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26942F\"></sup>to speak in other tongues <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26942G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26942G\"></sup>as the Spirit gave them utterance.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now there were dwelling in Jerusalem Jews, devout men from every nation under heaven.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26944H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26944H\"></sup>at this sound the multitude came together, and they were bewildered, because each one was hearing them speak in his own language.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26945I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26945I\"></sup>they were amazed and astonished, saying, “Are not all these who are speaking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26945J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26945J\"></sup>Galileans?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And how is it that we hear, each of us in his own native language?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Parthians and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26947K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26947K\"></sup>Medes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26947L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26947L\"></sup>Elamites and residents of Mesopotamia, Judea and Cappadocia, Pontus and Asia,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Phrygia and Pamphylia, Egypt and the parts of Libya belonging to Cyrene, and visitors from Rome,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>both Jews and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26949M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26949M\"></sup>proselytes, Cretans and Arabians—we hear them telling in our own tongues the mighty works of God.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26950N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26950N\"></sup>all were amazed and perplexed, saying to one another, “What does this mean?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But others <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26951O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26951O\"></sup>mocking said, “They are filled with new wine.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Peter, standing with the eleven, lifted up his voice and addressed them: “Men of Judea and all who dwell in Jerusalem, let this be known to you, and give ear to my words.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For these people are not drunk, as you suppose, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26953P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26953P\"></sup>since it is only the third hour of the day.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But this is what was uttered through the prophet Joel:",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26955Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26955Q\"></sup>“‘And in the last days it shall be, God declares,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26955R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26955R\"></sup>that I will pour out my Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26955S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26955S\"></sup>on all flesh,and your sons and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26955T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26955T\"></sup>your daughters shall prophesy,and your young men shall see visions,and your old men shall dream dreams;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>even on my male servants and female servantsin those days I will pour out my Spirit, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26956U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26956U\"></sup>they shall prophesy.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I will show wonders in the heavens aboveand signs on the earth below,blood, and fire, and vapor of smoke;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26958V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26958V\"></sup>the sun shall be turned to darknessand the moon to blood,before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26958W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26958W\"></sup>the day of the Lord comes, the great and magnificent day.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And it shall come to pass that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26959X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26959X\"></sup>everyone who calls upon the name of the Lord shall be saved.’",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Men of Israel, hear these words: Jesus of Nazareth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26960Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26960Y\"></sup>a man attested to you by God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26960Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26960Z\"></sup>with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26960AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26960AA\"></sup>mighty works and wonders and signs that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26960AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26960AB\"></sup>God did through him in your midst, as you yourselves know—",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>this Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26961AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26961AC\"></sup>delivered up according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26961AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26961AD\"></sup>the definite plan and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26961AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26961AE\"></sup>foreknowledge of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26961AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26961AF\"></sup>you crucified and killed by the hands of lawless men.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26962AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26962AG\"></sup>God raised him up, loosing the pangs of death, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26962AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26962AH\"></sup>it was not possible for him to be held by it.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For David says concerning him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26963AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26963AI\"></sup>“‘I saw the Lord always before me,for he is at my right hand that I may not be shaken;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>therefore my heart was glad, and my tongue rejoiced;my flesh also will dwell <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26964AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26964AJ\"></sup>in hope.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For you will not abandon my soul to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26965AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26965AK\"></sup>Hades,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26965AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26965AL\"></sup>or let your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26965AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26965AM\"></sup>Holy One <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26965AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26965AN\"></sup>see corruption.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>You have made known to me the paths of life;you will make me full of gladness with your presence.’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Brothers, I may say to you with confidence about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26967AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26967AO\"></sup>the patriarch David <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26967AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26967AP\"></sup>that he both died and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26967AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26967AQ\"></sup>was buried, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26967AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26967AR\"></sup>his tomb is with us to this day.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26968AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26968AS\"></sup>Being therefore a prophet, and knowing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26968AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26968AT\"></sup>God had sworn with an oath to him that he would set one of his descendants on his throne,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>he foresaw and spoke about the resurrection of the Christ, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26969AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26969AU\"></sup>he was not abandoned to Hades, nor did his flesh see corruption.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>This Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26970AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26970AV\"></sup>God raised up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26970AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26970AW\"></sup>and of that we all are witnesses.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26971AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26971AX\"></sup>Being therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26971AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26971AY\"></sup>exalted at the right hand of God, and having received from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26971AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26971AZ\"></sup>the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26971BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26971BA\"></sup>the promise of the Holy Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26971BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26971BB\"></sup>he has poured out this that you yourselves are seeing and hearing.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26972BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26972BC\"></sup>David did not ascend into the heavens, but he himself says,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26972BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26972BD\"></sup>“‘The Lord said to my Lord,“Sit at my right hand,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>until I make your enemies your footstool.”’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Let all the house of Israel therefore know for certain that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26974BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26974BE\"></sup>God has made him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26974BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26974BF\"></sup>both Lord and Christ, this Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26974BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26974BG\"></sup>whom you crucified.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Now when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26975BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26975BH\"></sup>they heard this they were cut to the heart, and said to Peter and the rest of the apostles, “Brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26975BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26975BI\"></sup>what shall we do?”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And Peter said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26976BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26976BJ\"></sup>“Repent and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26976BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26976BK\"></sup>be baptized every one of you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26976BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26976BL\"></sup>in the name of Jesus Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26976BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26976BM\"></sup>for the forgiveness of your sins, and you will receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26976BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26976BN\"></sup>the gift of the Holy Spirit.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26977BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26977BO\"></sup>the promise is for you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26977BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26977BP\"></sup>for your children and for all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26977BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26977BQ\"></sup>who are far off, everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26977BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26977BR\"></sup>whom the Lord our God calls to himself.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And with many other words he bore witness and continued to exhort them, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26978BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26978BS\"></sup>“Save yourselves from this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26978BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26978BT\"></sup>crooked generation.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>So those who received his word were baptized, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26979BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26979BU\"></sup>there were added that day about three thousand souls.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26980BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26980BV\"></sup>they devoted themselves to the apostles' <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26980BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26980BW\"></sup>teaching and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26980BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26980BX\"></sup>fellowship, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26980BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26980BY\"></sup>the breaking of bread and the prayers.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And awe came upon every soul, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26981BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26981BZ\"></sup>many wonders and signs were being done through the apostles.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And all who believed were together and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26982CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26982CA\"></sup>had all things in common.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26983CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26983CB\"></sup>they were selling their possessions and belongings and distributing the proceeds to all, as any had need.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And day by day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26984CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26984CC\"></sup>attending the temple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26984CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26984CD\"></sup>together and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26984CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26984CE\"></sup>breaking bread in their homes, they received their food <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26984CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26984CF\"></sup>with glad and generous hearts,",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>praising God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26985CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26985CG\"></sup>having favor with all the people. And the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26985CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26985CH\"></sup>added to their number <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26985CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26985CI\"></sup>day by day those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26985CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26985CJ\"></sup>were being saved."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Now Peter and John were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26986A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26986A\"></sup>going up to the temple at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26986B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26986B\"></sup>the hour of prayer, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26986C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26986C\"></sup>the ninth hour.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26987D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26987D\"></sup>lame from birth was being carried, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26987E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26987E\"></sup>whom they laid daily at the gate of the temple that is called the Beautiful Gate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26987F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26987F\"></sup>to ask alms of those entering the temple.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Seeing Peter and John about to go into the temple, he asked to receive alms.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Peter directed his gaze at him, as did John, and said, “Look at us.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he fixed his attention on them, expecting to receive something from them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But Peter said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26991G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26991G\"></sup>“I have no silver and gold, but what I do have I give to you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26991H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26991H\"></sup>In the name of Jesus Christ of Nazareth, rise up and walk!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he took him by the right hand and raised him up, and immediately his feet and ankles were made strong.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26993I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26993I\"></sup>leaping up, he stood and began to walk, and entered the temple with them, walking and leaping and praising God.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26994J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26994J\"></sup>all the people saw him walking and praising God,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and recognized him as the one who sat at the Beautiful Gate of the temple, asking for alms. And they were filled with wonder and amazement at what had happened to him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26996K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26996K\"></sup>While he clung to Peter and John, all the people, utterly astounded, ran together to them in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26996L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26996L\"></sup>the portico called Solomon's.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And when Peter saw it he addressed the people: “Men of Israel, why do you wonder at this, or why do you stare at us, as though by our own power or piety we have made him walk?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26998M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26998M\"></sup>The God of Abraham, the God of Isaac, and the God of Jacob, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26998N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26998N\"></sup>the God of our fathers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26998O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26998O\"></sup>glorified his servant Jesus, whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26998P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26998P\"></sup>you delivered over and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26998Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26998Q\"></sup>denied in the presence of Pilate, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26998R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26998R\"></sup>when he had decided to release him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But you denied <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26999S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26999S\"></sup>the Holy and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26999T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26999T\"></sup>Righteous One, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-26999U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-26999U\"></sup>asked for a murderer to be granted to you,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and you killed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27000V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27000V\"></sup>the Author of life, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27000W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27000W\"></sup>whom God raised from the dead. To this we are witnesses.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27001X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27001X\"></sup>his name—by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27001Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27001Y\"></sup>faith in his name—has made this man strong whom you see and know, and the faith that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27001Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27001Z\"></sup>through Jesus has given the man this perfect health in the presence of you all.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“And now, brothers, I know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27002AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27002AA\"></sup>you acted in ignorance, as did also your rulers.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But what God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27003AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27003AB\"></sup>foretold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27003AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27003AC\"></sup>by the mouth of all the prophets, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27003AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27003AD\"></sup>his Christ would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27003AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27003AE\"></sup>suffer, he thus fulfilled.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27004AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27004AF\"></sup>Repent therefore, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27004AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27004AG\"></sup>turn back, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27004AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27004AH\"></sup>your sins may be blotted out,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>that times of refreshing may come from the presence of the Lord, and that he may send the Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27005AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27005AI\"></sup>appointed for you, Jesus,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27006AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27006AJ\"></sup>whom heaven must receive until the time for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27006AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27006AK\"></sup>restoring all the things about which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27006AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27006AL\"></sup>God spoke by the mouth of his holy prophets long ago.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Moses said, ‘The Lord God will raise up for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27007AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27007AM\"></sup>a prophet like me from your brothers. You shall listen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27007AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27007AN\"></sup>to him in whatever he tells you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And it shall be that every soul who does not listen to that prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27008AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27008AO\"></sup>shall be destroyed from the people.’",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27009AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27009AP\"></sup>all the prophets who have spoken, from Samuel and those who came after him, also proclaimed these days.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27010AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27010AQ\"></sup>You are the sons of the prophets and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27010AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27010AR\"></sup>the covenant that God made with your fathers, saying to Abraham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27010AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27010AS\"></sup>‘And in your offspring shall all the families of the earth be blessed.’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27011AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27011AT\"></sup>God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27011AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27011AU\"></sup>having raised up his servant, sent him to you first, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27011AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27011AV\"></sup>to bless you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27011AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27011AW\"></sup>by turning every one of you from your wickedness.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>And as they were speaking to the people, the priests and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27012A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27012A\"></sup>the captain of the temple and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27012B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27012B\"></sup>the Sadducees came upon them,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>greatly annoyed because they were teaching the people and proclaiming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27013C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27013C\"></sup>in Jesus the resurrection from the dead.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And they arrested them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27014D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27014D\"></sup>put them in custody until the next day, for it was already evening.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But many of those who had heard the word believed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27015E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27015E\"></sup>the number of the men came to about five thousand.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>On the next day their rulers and elders and scribes gathered together in Jerusalem,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27017F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27017F\"></sup>Annas the high priest and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27017G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27017G\"></sup>Caiaphas and John and Alexander, and all who were of the high-priestly family.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And when they had set them in the midst, they inquired, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27018H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27018H\"></sup>“By what power or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27018I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27018I\"></sup>by what name did you do this?”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then Peter, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27019J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27019J\"></sup>filled with the Holy Spirit, said to them, “Rulers of the people and elders,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>if we are being examined today <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27020K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27020K\"></sup>concerning a good deed done to a crippled man, by what means this man has been healed,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>let it be known to all of you and to all the people of Israel that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27021L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27021L\"></sup>by the name of Jesus Christ of Nazareth, whom you crucified, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27021M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27021M\"></sup>whom God raised from the dead—by him this man is standing before you well.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27022N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27022N\"></sup>This Jesus is the stone that was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27022O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27022O\"></sup>rejected by you, the builders, which has become the cornerstone.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27023P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27023P\"></sup>salvation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27023Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27023Q\"></sup>in no one else, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27023R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27023R\"></sup>there is no other <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27023S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27023S\"></sup>name under heaven given among men by which we must be saved.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27024T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27024T\"></sup>Now when they saw the boldness of Peter and John, and perceived that they were uneducated, common men, they were astonished. And they recognized that they had been with Jesus.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But seeing the man who was healed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27025U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27025U\"></sup>standing beside them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27025V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27025V\"></sup>they had nothing to say in opposition.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But when they had commanded them to leave the council, they conferred with one another,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27027W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27027W\"></sup>“What shall we do with these men? For that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27027X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27027X\"></sup>a notable sign has been performed through them is evident to all the inhabitants of Jerusalem, and we cannot deny it.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But in order that it may spread no further among the people, let us warn them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27028Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27028Y\"></sup>to speak no more to anyone in this name.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So they called them and charged them not to speak or teach at all in the name of Jesus.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But Peter and John answered them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27030Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27030Z\"></sup>“Whether it is right in the sight of God to listen to you rather than to God, you must judge,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27031AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27031AA\"></sup>we cannot but speak of what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27031AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27031AB\"></sup>we have seen and heard.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And when they had further threatened them, they let them go, finding no way to punish them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27032AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27032AC\"></sup>because of the people, for all were praising God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27032AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27032AD\"></sup>for what had happened.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For the man on whom this sign of healing was performed was more than forty years old.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When they were released, they went to their friends and reported what the chief priests and the elders had said to them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And when they heard it, they lifted their voices <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27035AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27035AE\"></sup>together to God and said, “Sovereign Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27035AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27035AF\"></sup>who made the heaven and the earth and the sea and everything in them,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>who through the mouth of our father David, your servant, said by the Holy Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27036AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27036AG\"></sup>“‘Why did the Gentiles rage,and the peoples plot in vain?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The kings of the earth set themselves,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27037AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27037AH\"></sup>the rulers were gathered together,against the Lord and against his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27037AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27037AI\"></sup>Anointed’—",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>for truly in this city there were gathered together against your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27038AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27038AJ\"></sup>holy servant Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27038AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27038AK\"></sup>whom you anointed, both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27038AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27038AL\"></sup>Herod and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27038AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27038AM\"></sup>Pontius Pilate, along <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27038AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27038AN\"></sup>with the Gentiles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27038AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27038AO\"></sup>the peoples of Israel,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27039AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27039AP\"></sup>to do whatever your hand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27039AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27039AQ\"></sup>your plan had predestined to take place.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And now, Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27040AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27040AR\"></sup>look upon their threats and grant to your servants to continue to speak your word with all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27040AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27040AS\"></sup>boldness,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27041AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27041AT\"></sup>you stretch out your hand to heal, and signs and wonders are performed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27041AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27041AU\"></sup>through the name of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27041AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27041AV\"></sup>holy servant Jesus.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And when they had prayed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27042AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27042AW\"></sup>the place in which they were gathered together was shaken, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27042AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27042AX\"></sup>they were all filled with the Holy Spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27042AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27042AY\"></sup>continued to speak the word of God with boldness.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Now the full number of those who believed were of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27043AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27043AZ\"></sup>one heart and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27043BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27043BA\"></sup>soul, and no one said that any of the things that belonged to him was his own, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27043BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27043BB\"></sup>they had everything in common.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And with great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27044BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27044BC\"></sup>power the apostles were giving their testimony to the resurrection of the Lord Jesus, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27044BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27044BD\"></sup>great grace was upon them all.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27045BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27045BE\"></sup>There was not a needy person among them, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27045BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27045BF\"></sup>as many as were owners of lands or houses sold them and brought the proceeds of what was sold",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27046BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27046BG\"></sup>laid it at the apostles' feet, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27046BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27046BH\"></sup>it was distributed to each as any had need.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Thus Joseph, who was also called by the apostles Barnabas (which means <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27047BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27047BI\"></sup>son of encouragement), a Levite, a native of Cyprus,",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>sold a field that belonged to him and brought the money and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27048BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27048BJ\"></sup>laid it at the apostles' feet."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>But a man named Ananias, with his wife Sapphira, sold a piece of property,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and with his wife's knowledge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27050A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27050A\"></sup>he kept back for himself some of the proceeds and brought only a part of it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27050B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27050B\"></sup>laid it at the apostles' feet.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But Peter said, “Ananias, why has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27051C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27051C\"></sup>Satan filled your heart to lie <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27051D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27051D\"></sup>to the Holy Spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27051E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27051E\"></sup>to keep back for yourself part of the proceeds of the land?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>While it remained unsold, did it not remain your own? And after it was sold, was it not at your disposal? Why is it that you have contrived this deed in your heart? You have not lied to man but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27052F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27052F\"></sup>to God.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When Ananias heard these words, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27053G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27053G\"></sup>fell down and breathed his last. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27053H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27053H\"></sup>great fear came upon all who heard of it.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The young men rose and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27054I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27054I\"></sup>wrapped him up and carried him out and buried him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>After an interval of about three hours his wife came in, not knowing what had happened.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And Peter said to her, “Tell me whether you sold the land for so much.” And she said, “Yes, for so much.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But Peter said to her, “How is it that you have agreed together <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27057J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27057J\"></sup>to test <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27057K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27057K\"></sup>the Spirit of the Lord? Behold, the feet of those who have buried your husband are at the door, and they will carry you out.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Immediately she fell down at his feet and breathed her last. When the young men came in they found her dead, and they carried her out and buried her beside her husband.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27059L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27059L\"></sup>great fear came upon the whole church and upon all who heard of these things.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now many signs and wonders were regularly done among the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27060M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27060M\"></sup>by the hands of the apostles. And they were all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27060N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27060N\"></sup>together in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27060O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27060O\"></sup>Solomon's Portico.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>None of the rest dared join them, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27061P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27061P\"></sup>the people held them in high esteem.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27062Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27062Q\"></sup>more than ever believers were added to the Lord, multitudes of both men and women,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27063R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27063R\"></sup>so that they even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27063S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27063S\"></sup>carried out the sick into the streets and laid them on cots and mats, that as Peter came by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27063T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27063T\"></sup>at least his shadow might fall on some of them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The people also gathered from the towns around Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27064U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27064U\"></sup>bringing the sick and those afflicted with unclean spirits, and they were all healed.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But the high priest rose up, and all who were with him (that is, the party of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27065V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27065V\"></sup>the Sadducees), and filled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27065W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27065W\"></sup>jealousy",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>they arrested the apostles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27066X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27066X\"></sup>put them in the public prison.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But during the night <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27067Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27067Y\"></sup>an angel of the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27067Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27067Z\"></sup>opened the prison doors and brought them out, and said,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Go and stand in the temple and speak to the people all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27068AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27068AA\"></sup>the words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27068AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27068AB\"></sup>this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27068AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27068AC\"></sup>Life.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And when they heard this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27069AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27069AD\"></sup>they entered the temple <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27069AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27069AE\"></sup>at daybreak and began to teach.Now when the high priest came, and those who were with him, they called together the council, all the senate of the people of Israel, and sent to the prison to have them brought.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But when the officers came, they did not find them in the prison, so they returned and reported,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“We found the prison securely locked and the guards standing at the doors, but when we opened them we found no one inside.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27072AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27072AF\"></sup>the captain of the temple and the chief priests heard these words, they were greatly perplexed about them, wondering what this would come to.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And someone came and told them, “Look! The men whom you put in prison <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27073AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27073AG\"></sup>are standing in the temple and teaching the people.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27074AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27074AH\"></sup>the captain with the officers went and brought them, but not by force, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27074AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27074AI\"></sup>they were afraid of being stoned by the people.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And when they had brought them, they set them before the council. And the high priest questioned them,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27076AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27076AJ\"></sup>“We strictly charged you not to teach in this name, yet here you have filled Jerusalem with your teaching, and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27076AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27076AK\"></sup>intend to bring this man's blood upon us.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But Peter and the apostles answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27077AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27077AL\"></sup>“We must obey God rather than men.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27078AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27078AM\"></sup>The God of our fathers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27078AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27078AN\"></sup>raised Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27078AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27078AO\"></sup>whom you killed by hanging him on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27078AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27078AP\"></sup>a tree.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>God exalted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27079AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27079AQ\"></sup>him at his right hand as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27079AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27079AR\"></sup>Leader and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27079AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27079AS\"></sup>Savior, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27079AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27079AT\"></sup>to give <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27079AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27079AU\"></sup>repentance to Israel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27079AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27079AV\"></sup>forgiveness of sins.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27080AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27080AW\"></sup>we are witnesses to these things, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27080AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27080AX\"></sup>so is the Holy Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27080AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27080AY\"></sup>whom God has given to those who obey him.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>When they heard this, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27081AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27081AZ\"></sup>were enraged and wanted to kill them.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But a Pharisee in the council named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27082BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27082BA\"></sup>Gamaliel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27082BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27082BB\"></sup>a teacher of the law held in honor by all the people, stood up and gave orders to put the men outside for a little while.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And he said to them, “Men of Israel, take care what you are about to do with these men.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27084BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27084BC\"></sup>before these days Theudas rose up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27084BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27084BD\"></sup>claiming to be somebody, and a number of men, about four hundred, joined him. He was killed, and all who followed him were dispersed and came to nothing.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>After him Judas the Galilean rose up in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27085BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27085BE\"></sup>the census and drew away some of the people after him. He too perished, and all who followed him were scattered.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>So in the present case I tell you, keep away from these men and let them alone, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27086BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27086BF\"></sup>if this plan or this undertaking is of man, it will fail;",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27087BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27087BG\"></sup>if it is of God, you will not be able to overthrow them. You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27087BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27087BH\"></sup>might even be found opposing God!” So they took his advice,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27088BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27088BI\"></sup>when they had called in the apostles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27088BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27088BJ\"></sup>they beat them and charged them not to speak in the name of Jesus, and let them go.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Then they left the presence of the council, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27089BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27089BK\"></sup>rejoicing that they were counted worthy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27089BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27089BL\"></sup>to suffer dishonor for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27089BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27089BM\"></sup>the name.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And every day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27090BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27090BN\"></sup>in the temple and from house to house, they did not cease teaching and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27090BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27090BO\"></sup>preaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27090BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27090BP\"></sup>that the Christ is Jesus."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Now in these days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27091A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27091A\"></sup>when the disciples were increasing in number, a complaint by the Hellenists arose against the Hebrews because their widows were being neglected in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27091B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27091B\"></sup>the daily distribution.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the twelve summoned the full number of the disciples and said, “It is not right that we should give up preaching the word of God to serve tables.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27093C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27093C\"></sup>Therefore, brothers, pick out from among you seven men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27093D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27093D\"></sup>of good repute, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27093E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27093E\"></sup>full of the Spirit and of wisdom, whom we will appoint to this duty.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27094F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27094F\"></sup>we will devote ourselves to prayer and to the ministry of the word.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And what they said pleased the whole gathering, and they chose Stephen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27095G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27095G\"></sup>a man full of faith and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27095H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27095H\"></sup>of the Holy Spirit, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27095I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27095I\"></sup>Philip, and Prochorus, and Nicanor, and Timon, and Parmenas, and Nicolaus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27095J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27095J\"></sup>a proselyte of Antioch.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>These they set before the apostles, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27096K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27096K\"></sup>they prayed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27096L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27096L\"></sup>laid their hands on them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27097M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27097M\"></sup>the word of God continued to increase, and the number of the disciples multiplied greatly in Jerusalem, and a great many of the priests <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27097N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27097N\"></sup>became obedient to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27097O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27097O\"></sup>the faith.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And Stephen, full of grace and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27098P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27098P\"></sup>power, was doing great wonders and signs among the people.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then some of those who belonged to the synagogue of the Freedmen (as it was called), and of the Cyrenians, and of the Alexandrians, and of those from Cilicia and Asia, rose up and disputed with Stephen.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27100Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27100Q\"></sup>they could not withstand the wisdom and the Spirit with which he was speaking.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27101R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27101R\"></sup>they secretly instigated men who said, “We have heard him speak blasphemous words against Moses and God.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And they stirred up the people and the elders and the scribes, and they came upon him and seized him and brought him before the council,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27103S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27103S\"></sup>set up false <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27103T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27103T\"></sup>witnesses who said, “This man never ceases to speak words against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27103U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27103U\"></sup>this holy place and the law,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>for we have heard him say that this Jesus of Nazareth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27104V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27104V\"></sup>will destroy this place and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27104W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27104W\"></sup>change <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27104X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27104X\"></sup>the customs that Moses delivered to us.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And gazing at him, all who sat in the council saw that his face <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27105Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27105Y\"></sup>was like the face of an angel."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>And the high priest said, “Are these things so?”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And Stephen said:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27107A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27107A\"></sup>“Brothers and fathers, hear me. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27107B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27107B\"></sup>The God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27107C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27107C\"></sup>of glory appeared to our father Abraham when he was in Mesopotamia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27107D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27107D\"></sup>before he lived in Haran,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27108E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27108E\"></sup>‘Go out from your land and from your kindred and go into the land that I will show you.’",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27109F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27109F\"></sup>Then he went out from the land of the Chaldeans and lived in Haran. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27109G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27109G\"></sup>after his father died, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27109H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27109H\"></sup>God removed him from there into this land in which you are now living.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Yet he gave him no inheritance in it, not even a foot's length, but promised <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27110I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27110I\"></sup>to give it to him as a possession and to his offspring after him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27110J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27110J\"></sup>though he had no child.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And God spoke to this effect—that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27111K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27111K\"></sup>his offspring would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27111L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27111L\"></sup>be sojourners in a land belonging to others, who would enslave them and afflict them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27111M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27111M\"></sup>four hundred years.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>‘But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27112N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27112N\"></sup>I will judge the nation that they serve,’ said God, ‘and after that they shall come out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27112O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27112O\"></sup>and worship me in this place.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27113P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27113P\"></sup>he gave him the covenant of circumcision. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27113Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27113Q\"></sup>so Abraham became the father of Isaac, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27113R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27113R\"></sup>circumcised him on the eighth day, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27113S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27113S\"></sup>Isaac became the father of Jacob, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27113T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27113T\"></sup>Jacob of the twelve patriarchs.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“And the patriarchs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27114U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27114U\"></sup>jealous of Joseph, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27114V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27114V\"></sup>sold him into Egypt; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27114W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27114W\"></sup>God was with him",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and rescued him out of all his afflictions and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27115X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27115X\"></sup>gave him favor and wisdom before Pharaoh, king of Egypt, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27115Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27115Y\"></sup>who made him ruler over Egypt and over all his household.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27116Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27116Z\"></sup>there came a famine throughout all Egypt and Canaan, and great affliction, and our fathers could find no food.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27117AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27117AA\"></sup>But when Jacob heard that there was grain in Egypt, he sent out our fathers on their first visit.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27118AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27118AB\"></sup>on the second visit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27118AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27118AC\"></sup>Joseph made himself known to his brothers, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27118AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27118AD\"></sup>Joseph's family became known to Pharaoh.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27119AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27119AE\"></sup>Joseph sent and summoned Jacob his father and all his kindred, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27119AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27119AF\"></sup>seventy-five persons in all.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27120AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27120AG\"></sup>Jacob went down into Egypt, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27120AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27120AH\"></sup>he died, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27120AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27120AI\"></sup>and our fathers,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27121AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27121AJ\"></sup>they were carried back to Shechem and laid in the tomb that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27121AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27121AK\"></sup>Abraham had bought for a sum of silver from the sons of Hamor in Shechem.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27122AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27122AL\"></sup>as the time of the promise drew near, which God had granted to Abraham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27122AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27122AM\"></sup>the people increased and multiplied in Egypt",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>until there arose over Egypt another king <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27123AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27123AN\"></sup>who did not know Joseph.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27124AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27124AO\"></sup>He dealt shrewdly with our race and forced our fathers to expose their infants, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27124AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27124AP\"></sup>so that they would not be kept alive.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27125AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27125AQ\"></sup>At this time Moses was born; and he was beautiful in God's sight. And he was brought up for three months in his father's house,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27126AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27126AR\"></sup>when he was exposed, Pharaoh's daughter adopted him and brought him up as her own son.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And Moses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27127AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27127AS\"></sup>was instructed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27127AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27127AT\"></sup>all the wisdom of the Egyptians, and he was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27127AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27127AU\"></sup>mighty in his words and deeds.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“When he was forty years old, it came into his heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27128AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27128AV\"></sup>to visit his brothers, the children of Israel.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And seeing one of them being wronged, he defended the oppressed man and avenged him by striking down the Egyptian.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He supposed that his brothers would understand that God was giving them salvation by his hand, but they did not understand.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27131AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27131AW\"></sup>And on the following day he appeared to them as they were quarreling and tried to reconcile them, saying, ‘Men, you are brothers. Why do you wrong each other?’",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But the man who was wronging his neighbor thrust him aside, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27132AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27132AX\"></sup>‘Who made you a ruler and a judge over us?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do you want to kill me as you killed the Egyptian yesterday?’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>At this retort <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27134AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27134AY\"></sup>Moses fled and became an exile in the land of Midian, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27134AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27134AZ\"></sup>where he became the father of two sons.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Now when forty years had passed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27135BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27135BA\"></sup>an angel appeared to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27135BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27135BB\"></sup>in the wilderness of Mount Sinai, in a flame of fire in a bush.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>When Moses saw it, he was amazed at the sight, and as he drew near to look, there came the voice of the Lord:",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27137BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27137BC\"></sup>‘I am the God of your fathers, the God of Abraham and of Isaac and of Jacob.’ And Moses trembled and did not dare to look.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Then the Lord said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27138BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27138BD\"></sup>‘Take off the sandals from your feet, for the place where you are standing is holy ground.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27139BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27139BE\"></sup>I have surely seen the affliction of my people who are in Egypt, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27139BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27139BF\"></sup>have heard their groaning, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27139BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27139BG\"></sup>I have come down to deliver them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27139BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27139BH\"></sup>And now come, I will send you to Egypt.’",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>“This Moses, whom they rejected, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27140BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27140BI\"></sup>saying, ‘Who made you a ruler and a judge?’—this man God sent as both ruler and redeemer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27140BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27140BJ\"></sup>by the hand of the angel who appeared to him in the bush.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27141BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27141BK\"></sup>This man led them out, performing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27141BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27141BL\"></sup>wonders and signs <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27141BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27141BM\"></sup>in Egypt and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27141BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27141BN\"></sup>at the Red Sea and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27141BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27141BO\"></sup>in the wilderness for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27141BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27141BP\"></sup>forty years.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>This is the Moses who said to the Israelites, ‘God will raise up for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27142BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27142BQ\"></sup>a prophet like me from your brothers.’",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>This is the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27143BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27143BR\"></sup>who was in the congregation in the wilderness with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27143BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27143BS\"></sup>the angel who spoke to him at Mount Sinai, and with our fathers. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27143BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27143BT\"></sup>He received <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27143BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27143BU\"></sup>living <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27143BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27143BV\"></sup>oracles to give to us.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Our fathers refused to obey him, but thrust him aside, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27144BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27144BW\"></sup>in their hearts they turned to Egypt,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>saying to Aaron, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27145BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27145BX\"></sup>‘Make for us gods who will go before us. As for this Moses who led us out from the land of Egypt, we do not know what has become of him.’",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27146BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27146BY\"></sup>they made a calf in those days, and offered a sacrifice to the idol and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27146BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27146BZ\"></sup>were rejoicing in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27146CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27146CA\"></sup>the works of their hands.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27147CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27147CB\"></sup>God turned away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27147CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27147CC\"></sup>gave them over to worship <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27147CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27147CD\"></sup>the host of heaven, as it is written in the book of the prophets:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27147CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27147CE\"></sup>“‘Did you bring to me slain beasts and sacrifices,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27147CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27147CF\"></sup>during the forty years in the wilderness, O house of Israel?",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>You took up the tent of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27148CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27148CG\"></sup>Molochand the star of your god Rephan,the images that you made to worship;and I will send you into exile beyond Babylon.’",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“Our fathers had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27149CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27149CH\"></sup>the tent of witness in the wilderness, just as he who spoke to Moses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27149CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27149CI\"></sup>directed him to make it, according to the pattern that he had seen.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Our fathers in turn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27150CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27150CJ\"></sup>brought it in with Joshua when they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27150CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27150CK\"></sup>dispossessed the nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27150CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27150CL\"></sup>that God drove out before our fathers. So it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27150CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27150CM\"></sup>until the days of David,",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27151CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27151CN\"></sup>who found favor in the sight of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27151CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27151CO\"></sup>asked to find a dwelling place for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27151CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27151CP\"></sup>the God of Jacob.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>But it was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27152CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27152CQ\"></sup>Solomon who built a house for him.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27153CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27153CR\"></sup>Yet the Most High does not dwell <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27153CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27153CS\"></sup>in houses made by hands, as the prophet says,",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27154CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27154CT\"></sup>“‘Heaven is my throne,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27154CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27154CU\"></sup>and the earth is my footstool.What kind of house will you build for me, says the Lord,or what is the place of my rest?",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>Did not my hand make all these things?’",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27156CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27156CV\"></sup>“You stiff-necked people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27156CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27156CW\"></sup>uncircumcised in heart and ears, you always resist the Holy Spirit. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27156CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27156CX\"></sup>As your fathers did, so do you.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27157CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27157CY\"></sup>Which of the prophets did your fathers not persecute? And they killed those who announced beforehand the coming of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27157CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27157CZ\"></sup>the Righteous One, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27157DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27157DA\"></sup>whom you have now betrayed and murdered,",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>you who received the law <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27158DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27158DB\"></sup>as delivered by angels and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27158DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27158DC\"></sup>did not keep it.”",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>Now when they heard these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27159DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27159DD\"></sup>they were enraged, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27159DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27159DE\"></sup>ground their teeth at him.",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>But he, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27160DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27160DF\"></sup>full of the Holy Spirit, gazed into heaven and saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27160DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27160DG\"></sup>the glory of God, and Jesus standing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27160DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27160DH\"></sup>at the right hand of God.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>And he said, “Behold, I see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27161DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27161DI\"></sup>the heavens opened, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27161DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27161DJ\"></sup>the Son of Man standing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27161DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27161DK\"></sup>at the right hand of God.”",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>But they cried out with a loud voice and stopped their ears and rushed together at him.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27163DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27163DL\"></sup>they cast him out of the city and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27163DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27163DM\"></sup>stoned him. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27163DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27163DN\"></sup>the witnesses laid down their garments <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27163DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27163DO\"></sup>at the feet of a young man named Saul.",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>And as they were stoning Stephen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27164DP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DP&quot;&gt;DP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27164DP\"></sup>he called out, “Lord Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27164DQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DQ&quot;&gt;DQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27164DQ\"></sup>receive my spirit.”",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27165DR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DR&quot;&gt;DR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27165DR\"></sup>falling to his knees he cried out with a loud voice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27165DS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DS&quot;&gt;DS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27165DS\"></sup>“Lord, do not hold this sin against them.” And when he had said this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27165DT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DT&quot;&gt;DT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27165DT\"></sup>he fell asleep."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27166A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27166A\"></sup>Saul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27166B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27166B\"></sup>approved of his execution.And there arose on that day a great persecution against the church in Jerusalem, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27166C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27166C\"></sup>they were all scattered throughout the regions of Judea and Samaria, except the apostles.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Devout men buried Stephen and made great lamentation over him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27168D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27168D\"></sup>Saul was ravaging the church, and entering house after house, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27168E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27168E\"></sup>dragged off men and women and committed them to prison.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27169F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27169F\"></sup>those who were scattered went about preaching the word.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27170G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27170G\"></sup>Philip went down to the city of Samaria and proclaimed to them the Christ.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27171H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27171H\"></sup>And the crowds with one accord paid attention to what was being said by Philip, when they heard him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27171I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27171I\"></sup>and saw the signs that he did.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27172J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27172J\"></sup>unclean spirits, crying out with a loud voice, came out of many who had them, and many who were paralyzed or lame were healed.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27173K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27173K\"></sup>there was much joy in that city.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But there was a man named Simon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27174L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27174L\"></sup>who had previously practiced magic in the city and amazed the people of Samaria, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27174M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27174M\"></sup>saying that he himself was somebody great.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They all paid attention to him, from the least to the greatest, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27175N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27175N\"></sup>“This man is the power of God that is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27175O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27175O\"></sup>Great.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And they paid attention to him because for a long time he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27176P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27176P\"></sup>amazed them with his magic.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27177Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27177Q\"></sup>they believed Philip as he preached good news <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27177R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27177R\"></sup>about the kingdom of God and the name of Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27177S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27177S\"></sup>they were baptized, both men and women.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Even Simon himself believed, and after being baptized he continued with Philip. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27178T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27178T\"></sup>seeing signs and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27178U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27178U\"></sup>great miracles performed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27178V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27178V\"></sup>he was amazed.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Now when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27179W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27179W\"></sup>the apostles at Jerusalem heard that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27179X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27179X\"></sup>Samaria had received the word of God, they sent to them Peter and John,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>who came down and prayed for them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27180Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27180Y\"></sup>that they might receive the Holy Spirit,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27181Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27181Z\"></sup>he had not yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27181AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27181AA\"></sup>fallen on any of them, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27181AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27181AB\"></sup>they had only been baptized in the name of the Lord Jesus.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27182AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27182AC\"></sup>they laid their hands on them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27182AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27182AD\"></sup>they received the Holy Spirit.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now when Simon saw that the Spirit was given through the laying on of the apostles' hands, he offered them money,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>saying, “Give me this power also, so that anyone on whom I lay my hands may receive the Holy Spirit.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But Peter said to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27185AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27185AE\"></sup>“May your silver perish with you, because you thought you could obtain the gift of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27185AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27185AF\"></sup>with money!",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You have neither part nor lot in this matter, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27186AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27186AG\"></sup>your heart is not right before God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Repent, therefore, of this wickedness of yours, and pray to the Lord that, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27187AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27187AH\"></sup>if possible, the intent of your heart may be forgiven you.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For I see that you are in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27188AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27188AI\"></sup>the gall of bitterness and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27188AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27188AJ\"></sup>the bond of iniquity.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And Simon answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27189AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27189AK\"></sup>“Pray for me to the Lord, that nothing of what you have said may come upon me.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now when they had testified and spoken the word of the Lord, they returned to Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27190AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27190AL\"></sup>preaching the gospel to many villages of the Samaritans.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27191AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27191AM\"></sup>an angel of the Lord said to Philip, “Rise and go toward the south to the road that goes down from Jerusalem to Gaza.” This is a desert place.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And he rose and went. And there was an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27192AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27192AN\"></sup>Ethiopian, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27192AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27192AO\"></sup>eunuch, a court official of Candace, queen of the Ethiopians, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27192AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27192AP\"></sup>who was in charge of all her treasure. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27192AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27192AQ\"></sup>He had come to Jerusalem to worship",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>and was returning, seated in his chariot, and he was reading the prophet Isaiah.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And the Spirit said to Philip, “Go over and join this chariot.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>So Philip ran to him and heard him reading Isaiah the prophet and asked, “Do you understand what you are reading?”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27196AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27196AR\"></sup>“How can I, unless someone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27196AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27196AS\"></sup>guides me?” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27196AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27196AT\"></sup>he invited Philip to come up and sit with him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Now the passage of the Scripture that he was reading was this:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27197AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27197AU\"></sup>“Like a sheep he was led to the slaughterand like a lamb before its shearer is silent,so he opens not his mouth.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>In his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27198AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27198AV\"></sup>humiliation justice was denied him.Who can describe his generation?For his life is taken away from the earth.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And the eunuch said to Philip, “About whom, I ask you, does the prophet say this, about himself or about someone else?”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Then Philip opened his mouth, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27200AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27200AW\"></sup>beginning with this Scripture <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27200AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27200AX\"></sup>he told him the good news about Jesus.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And as they were going along the road they came to some water, and the eunuch said, “See, here is water! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27201AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27201AY\"></sup>What prevents me from being baptized?”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And he commanded the chariot to stop, and they both went down into the water, Philip and the eunuch, and he baptized him.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And when they came up out of the water, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27203AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27203AZ\"></sup>the Spirit of the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27203BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27203BA\"></sup>carried Philip away, and the eunuch saw him no more, and went on his way rejoicing.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>But Philip found himself at Azotus, and as he passed through he preached the gospel to all the towns until he came to Caesarea."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>But Saul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27205A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27205A\"></sup>still <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27205B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27205B\"></sup>breathing threats and murder against the disciples of the Lord, went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27205C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27205C\"></sup>the high priest",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and asked him for letters <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27206D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27206D\"></sup>to the synagogues at Damascus, so that if he found any belonging to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27206E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27206E\"></sup>the Way, men or women, he might bring them bound to Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27207F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27207F\"></sup>Now as he went on his way, he approached Damascus, and suddenly a light from heaven shone around him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And falling to the ground, he heard a voice saying to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Saul, Saul, why are you persecuting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27208G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27208G\"></sup>me?”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he said, “Who are you, Lord?” And he said, <span class=\"woj\">“I am Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27209H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27209H\"></sup>whom you are persecuting.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27210I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27210I\"></sup>rise and enter the city, and you will be told <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27210J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27210J\"></sup>what you are to do.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27211K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27211K\"></sup>The men who were traveling with him stood speechless, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27211L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27211L\"></sup>hearing the voice but seeing no one.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Saul rose from the ground, and although his eyes were opened, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27212M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27212M\"></sup>he saw nothing. So they led him by the hand and brought him into Damascus.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And for three days he was without sight, and neither ate nor drank.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now there was a disciple at Damascus named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27214N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27214N\"></sup>Ananias. The Lord said to him in a vision, <span class=\"woj\">“Ananias.”</span> And he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27214O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27214O\"></sup>“Here I am, Lord.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the Lord said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Rise and go to the street called Straight, and at the house of Judas look for a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27215P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27215P\"></sup>of Tarsus named Saul, for behold, he is praying,</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and he has seen in a vision a man named Ananias come in and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27216Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27216Q\"></sup>lay his hands on him so that he might regain his sight.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But Ananias answered, “Lord, I have heard from many about this man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27217R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27217R\"></sup>how much evil he has done to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27217S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27217S\"></sup>your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27217T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27217T\"></sup>saints at Jerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And here he has authority from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27218U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27218U\"></sup>the chief priests to bind all who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27218V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27218V\"></sup>call on your name.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But the Lord said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Go, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27219W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27219W\"></sup>he is a chosen instrument of mine to carry my name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27219X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27219X\"></sup>before the Gentiles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27219Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27219Y\"></sup>kings and the children of Israel.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27220Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27220Z\"></sup>I will show him how much <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27220AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27220AA\"></sup>he must suffer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27220AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27220AB\"></sup>for the sake of my name.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27221AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27221AC\"></sup>Ananias departed and entered the house. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27221AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27221AD\"></sup>laying his hands on him he said, “Brother Saul, the Lord Jesus who appeared to you on the road by which you came has sent me so that you may regain your sight and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27221AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27221AE\"></sup>be filled with the Holy Spirit.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And immediately something like scales fell from his eyes, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27222AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27222AF\"></sup>he regained his sight. Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27222AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27222AG\"></sup>he rose and was baptized;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27223AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27223AH\"></sup>taking food, he was strengthened.For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27223AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27223AI\"></sup>some days he was with the disciples at Damascus.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And immediately he proclaimed Jesus in the synagogues, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27224AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27224AJ\"></sup>“He is the Son of God.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And all who heard him were amazed and said, “Is not this the man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27225AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27225AK\"></sup>made havoc <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27225AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27225AL\"></sup>in Jerusalem of those who called upon this name? And has he not come here for this purpose, to bring them bound before the chief priests?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But Saul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27226AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27226AM\"></sup>increased all the more in strength, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27226AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27226AN\"></sup>confounded the Jews who lived in Damascus by proving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27226AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27226AO\"></sup>that Jesus was the Christ.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27227AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27227AP\"></sup>When many days had passed, the Jews plotted to kill him,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27228AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27228AQ\"></sup>plot became known to Saul. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27228AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27228AR\"></sup>They were watching the gates day and night in order to kill him,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>but his disciples took him by night and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27229AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27229AS\"></sup>let him down through an opening in the wall, lowering him in a basket.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27230AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27230AT\"></sup>when he had come to Jerusalem, he attempted to join the disciples. And they were all afraid of him, for they did not believe that he was a disciple.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27231AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27231AU\"></sup>Barnabas took him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27231AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27231AV\"></sup>brought him to the apostles and declared to them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27231AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27231AW\"></sup>how on the road he had seen the Lord, who spoke to him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27231AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27231AX\"></sup>how at Damascus he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27231AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27231AY\"></sup>preached boldly in the name of Jesus.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So he went <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27232AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27232AZ\"></sup>in and out among them at Jerusalem, preaching boldly in the name of the Lord.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And he spoke and disputed against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27233BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27233BA\"></sup>the Hellenists. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27233BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27233BB\"></sup>they were seeking to kill him.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27234BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27234BC\"></sup>the brothers learned this, they brought him down to Caesarea and sent him off <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27234BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27234BD\"></sup>to Tarsus.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27235BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27235BE\"></sup>the church throughout all Judea and Galilee and Samaria had peace and was being built up. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27235BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27235BF\"></sup>walking in the fear of the Lord and in the comfort of the Holy Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27235BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27235BG\"></sup>it multiplied.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27236BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27236BH\"></sup>as Peter went here and there among them all, he came down also to the saints who lived at Lydda.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>There he found a man named Aeneas, bedridden for eight years, who was paralyzed.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And Peter said to him, “Aeneas, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27238BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27238BI\"></sup>Jesus Christ heals you; rise and make your bed.” And immediately he rose.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27239BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27239BJ\"></sup>And all the residents of Lydda and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27239BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27239BK\"></sup>Sharon saw him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27239BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27239BL\"></sup>they turned to the Lord.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Now there was in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27240BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27240BM\"></sup>Joppa a disciple named Tabitha, which, translated, means Dorcas. She was full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27240BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27240BN\"></sup>good works and acts of charity.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>In those days she became ill and died, and when they had washed her, they laid her in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27241BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27241BO\"></sup>an upper room.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Since Lydda was near Joppa, the disciples, hearing that Peter was there, sent two men to him, urging him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27242BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27242BP\"></sup>“Please come to us without delay.”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>So Peter rose and went with them. And when he arrived, they took him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27243BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27243BQ\"></sup>the upper room. All the widows stood beside him weeping and showing tunics and other garments that Dorcas made while she was with them.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>But Peter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27244BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27244BR\"></sup>put them all outside, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27244BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27244BS\"></sup>knelt down and prayed; and turning to the body <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27244BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27244BT\"></sup>he said, “Tabitha, arise.” And she opened her eyes, and when she saw Peter she sat up.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And he gave her his hand and raised her up. Then, calling the saints and widows, he presented her alive.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And it became known throughout all Joppa, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27246BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27246BU\"></sup>many believed in the Lord.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And he stayed in Joppa for many days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27247BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27247BV\"></sup>with one Simon, a tanner."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>At Caesarea there was a man named Cornelius, a centurion of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27248A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27248A\"></sup>what was known as the Italian Cohort,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>a devout man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27249B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27249B\"></sup>who feared God with all his household, gave alms generously to the people, and prayed continually to God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27250C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27250C\"></sup>About the ninth hour of the day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27250D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27250D\"></sup>he saw clearly in a vision <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27250E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27250E\"></sup>an angel of God come in and say to him, “Cornelius.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And he stared at him in terror and said, “What is it, Lord?” And he said to him, “Your prayers and your alms <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27251F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27251F\"></sup>have ascended <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27251G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27251G\"></sup>as a memorial before God.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And now send men to Joppa and bring one Simon who is called Peter.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He is lodging <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27253H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27253H\"></sup>with one Simon, a tanner, whose house is by the sea.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When the angel who spoke to him had departed, he called two of his servants and a devout soldier from among those who attended him,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and having related everything to them, he sent them to Joppa.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The next day, as they were on their journey and approaching the city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27256I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27256I\"></sup>Peter went up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27256J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27256J\"></sup>on the housetop about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27256K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27256K\"></sup>the sixth hour to pray.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And he became hungry and wanted something to eat, but while they were preparing it, he fell into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27257L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27257L\"></sup>a trance",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27258M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27258M\"></sup>the heavens opened and something like a great sheet descending, being let down by its four corners upon the earth.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In it were all kinds of animals and reptiles and birds of the air.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And there came a voice to him: <span class=\"woj\">“Rise, Peter; kill and eat.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Peter said, “By no means, Lord; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27261N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27261N\"></sup>for I have never eaten anything that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27261O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27261O\"></sup>common or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27261P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27261P\"></sup>unclean.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the voice came to him again a second time, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27262Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27262Q\"></sup>“What God has made clean, do not call common.”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>This happened three times, and the thing was taken up at once to heaven.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now while Peter was inwardly perplexed as to what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27264R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27264R\"></sup>the vision that he had seen might mean, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27264S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27264S\"></sup>the men who were sent by Cornelius, having made inquiry for Simon's house, stood at the gate",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and called out to ask whether Simon who was called Peter was lodging there.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And while Peter was pondering <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27266T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27266T\"></sup>the vision, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27266U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27266U\"></sup>the Spirit said to him, “Behold, three men are looking for you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Rise and go down and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27267V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27267V\"></sup>accompany them without hesitation, for I have sent them.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And Peter went down to the men and said, “I am the one you are looking for. What is the reason for your coming?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And they said, “Cornelius, a centurion, an upright and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27269W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27269W\"></sup>God-fearing man, who is well spoken of by the whole Jewish nation, was directed by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27269X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27269X\"></sup>a holy angel to send for you to come to his house and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27269Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27269Y\"></sup>to hear what you have to say.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>So he invited them in to be his guests.The next day he rose and went away with them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27270Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27270Z\"></sup>some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27270AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27270AA\"></sup>the brothers from Joppa accompanied him.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And on the following day they entered Caesarea. Cornelius was expecting them and had called together his relatives and close friends.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When Peter entered, Cornelius met him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27272AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27272AB\"></sup>fell down at his feet and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27272AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27272AC\"></sup>worshiped him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But Peter lifted him up, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27273AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27273AD\"></sup>“Stand up; I too am a man.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And as he talked with him, he went in and found many persons gathered.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And he said to them, “You yourselves know how unlawful it is for a Jew <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27275AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27275AE\"></sup>to associate with or to visit anyone of another nation, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27275AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27275AF\"></sup>God has shown me that I should not call any person common or unclean.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So when I was sent for, I came without objection. I ask then why you sent for me.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And Cornelius said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27277AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27277AG\"></sup>“Four days ago, about this hour, I was praying in my house at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27277AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27277AH\"></sup>the ninth hour, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27277AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27277AI\"></sup>a man stood before me in bright clothing",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>and said, ‘Cornelius, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27278AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27278AJ\"></sup>your prayer has been heard and your alms have been remembered before God.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Send therefore to Joppa and ask for Simon who is called Peter. He is lodging in the house of Simon, a tanner, by the sea.’",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So I sent for you at once, and you have been kind enough to come. Now therefore we are all here in the presence of God to hear all that you have been commanded by the Lord.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>So Peter opened his mouth and said: “Truly I understand that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27281AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27281AK\"></sup>God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27281AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27281AL\"></sup>shows no partiality,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27282AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27282AM\"></sup>in every nation anyone who fears him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27282AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27282AN\"></sup>does what is right is acceptable to him.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>As for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27283AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27283AO\"></sup>the word that he sent to Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27283AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27283AP\"></sup>preaching good news of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27283AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27283AQ\"></sup>peace through Jesus Christ (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27283AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27283AR\"></sup>he is Lord of all),",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>you yourselves know what happened throughout all Judea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27284AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27284AS\"></sup>beginning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27284AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27284AT\"></sup>from Galilee after the baptism that John proclaimed:",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>how <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27285AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27285AU\"></sup>God anointed Jesus of Nazareth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27285AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27285AV\"></sup>with the Holy Spirit and with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27285AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27285AW\"></sup>power. He went about doing good and healing all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27285AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27285AX\"></sup>who were oppressed by the devil, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27285AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27285AY\"></sup>for God was with him.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27286AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27286AZ\"></sup>we are witnesses of all that he did both in the country of the Jews and in Jerusalem. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27286BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27286BA\"></sup>They put him to death by hanging him on a tree,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27287BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27287BB\"></sup>God raised him on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27287BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27287BC\"></sup>the third day and made him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27287BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27287BD\"></sup>appear,",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27288BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27288BE\"></sup>not to all the people but to us who had been chosen by God as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27288BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27288BF\"></sup>witnesses, who ate and drank with him after he rose from the dead.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27289BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27289BG\"></sup>he commanded us to preach to the people and to testify <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27289BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27289BH\"></sup>that he is the one appointed by God to be judge <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27289BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27289BI\"></sup>of the living and the dead.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27290BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27290BJ\"></sup>To him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27290BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27290BK\"></sup>all the prophets bear witness that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27290BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27290BL\"></sup>everyone who believes in him receives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27290BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27290BM\"></sup>forgiveness of sins <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27290BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27290BN\"></sup>through his name.”",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>While Peter was still saying these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27291BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27291BO\"></sup>the Holy Spirit fell on all who heard the word.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>And the believers from among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27292BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27292BP\"></sup>the circumcised who had come with Peter were amazed, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27292BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27292BQ\"></sup>the gift of the Holy Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27292BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27292BR\"></sup>was poured out even on the Gentiles.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>For they were hearing them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27293BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27293BS\"></sup>speaking in tongues and extolling God. Then Peter declared,",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27294BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27294BT\"></sup>“Can anyone withhold water for baptizing these people, who have received the Holy Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27294BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27294BU\"></sup>just as we have?”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27295BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27295BV\"></sup>commanded them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27295BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27295BW\"></sup>to be baptized in the name of Jesus Christ. Then they asked him to remain for some days."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Now the apostles and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27296A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27296A\"></sup>the brothers who were throughout Judea heard that the Gentiles also had received the word of God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So when Peter went up to Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27297B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27297B\"></sup>the circumcision party criticized him, saying,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27298C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27298C\"></sup>“You went to uncircumcised men and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27298D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27298D\"></sup>ate with them.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But Peter began and explained it to them in order:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27300E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27300E\"></sup>“I was in the city of Joppa praying, and in a trance I saw a vision, something like a great sheet descending, being let down from heaven by its four corners, and it came down to me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Looking at it closely, I observed animals and beasts of prey and reptiles and birds of the air.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And I heard a voice saying to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Rise, Peter; kill and eat.’</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But I said, ‘By no means, Lord; for nothing common or unclean has ever entered my mouth.’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But the voice answered a second time from heaven, <span class=\"woj\">‘What God has made clean, do not call common.’</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This happened three times, and all was drawn up again into heaven.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And behold, at that very moment three men arrived at the house in which we were, sent to me from Caesarea.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And the Spirit told me to go with them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27307F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27307F\"></sup>making no distinction. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27307G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27307G\"></sup>These six brothers also accompanied me, and we entered the man's house.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And he told us how he had seen the angel stand in his house and say, ‘Send to Joppa and bring Simon who is called Peter;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27309H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27309H\"></sup>he will declare to you a message by which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27309I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27309I\"></sup>you will be saved, you and all your household.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>As I began to speak, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27310J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27310J\"></sup>the Holy Spirit fell on them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27310K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27310K\"></sup>just as on us at the beginning.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And I remembered the word of the Lord, how he said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27311L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27311L\"></sup>‘John baptized with water, but you will be baptized with the Holy Spirit.’</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27312M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27312M\"></sup>God gave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27312N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27312N\"></sup>the same gift to them as he gave to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27312O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27312O\"></sup>when we believed in the Lord Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27312P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27312P\"></sup>who was I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27312Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27312Q\"></sup>that I could stand in God's way?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When they heard these things they fell silent. And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27313R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27313R\"></sup>glorified God, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27313S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27313S\"></sup>“Then to the Gentiles also God has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27313T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27313T\"></sup>granted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27313U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27313U\"></sup>repentance that leads to life.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27314V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27314V\"></sup>Now those who were scattered because of the persecution that arose over Stephen traveled as far as Phoenicia and Cyprus and Antioch, speaking the word to no one except Jews.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But there were some of them, men of Cyprus and Cyrene, who on coming to Antioch spoke to the Hellenists also, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27315W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27315W\"></sup>preaching the Lord Jesus.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27316X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27316X\"></sup>the hand of the Lord was with them, and a great number who believed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27316Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27316Y\"></sup>turned to the Lord.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The report of this came to the ears of the church in Jerusalem, and they sent Barnabas to Antioch.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When he came and saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27318Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27318Z\"></sup>the grace of God, he was glad, and he exhorted them all to remain faithful to the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27318AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27318AA\"></sup>with steadfast purpose,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>for he was a good man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27319AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27319AB\"></sup>full of the Holy Spirit and of faith. And a great many people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27319AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27319AC\"></sup>were added to the Lord.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So Barnabas went to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27320AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27320AD\"></sup>Tarsus to look for Saul,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and when he had found him, he brought him to Antioch. For a whole year they met with the church and taught a great many people. And in Antioch the disciples were first called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27321AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27321AE\"></sup>Christians.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Now in these days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27322AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27322AF\"></sup>prophets came down from Jerusalem to Antioch.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And one of them named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27323AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27323AG\"></sup>Agabus stood up and foretold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27323AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27323AH\"></sup>by the Spirit that there would be a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27323AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27323AI\"></sup>famine over all the world (this took place in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27323AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27323AJ\"></sup>Claudius).",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So the disciples determined, every one according to his ability, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27324AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27324AK\"></sup>to send relief to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27324AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27324AL\"></sup>the brothers living in Judea.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27325AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27325AM\"></sup>And they did so, sending it to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27325AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27325AN\"></sup>the elders by the hand of Barnabas and Saul."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>About that time Herod the king laid violent hands on some who belonged to the church.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He killed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27327A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27327A\"></sup>James the brother of John <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27327B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27327B\"></sup>with the sword,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and when he saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27328C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27328C\"></sup>that it pleased the Jews, he proceeded to arrest Peter also. This was during <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27328D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27328D\"></sup>the days of Unleavened Bread.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And when he had seized him, he put him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27329E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27329E\"></sup>in prison, delivering him over to four <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27329F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27329F\"></sup>squads of soldiers to guard him, intending after the Passover to bring him out to the people.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So Peter was kept in prison, but earnest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27330G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27330G\"></sup>prayer for him was made to God by the church.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now when Herod was about to bring him out, on that very night, Peter was sleeping between two soldiers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27331H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27331H\"></sup>bound with two chains, and sentries before the door were guarding the prison.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27332I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27332I\"></sup>an angel of the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27332J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27332J\"></sup>stood next to him, and a light shone in the cell. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27332K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27332K\"></sup>He struck Peter on the side and woke him, saying, “Get up quickly.” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27332L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27332L\"></sup>the chains fell off his hands.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the angel said to him, “Dress yourself and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27333M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27333M\"></sup>put on your sandals.” And he did so. And he said to him, “Wrap your cloak around you and follow me.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And he went out and followed him. He did not know that what was being done by the angel was real, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27334N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27334N\"></sup>thought he was seeing a vision.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When they had passed the first and the second guard, they came to the iron gate leading into the city. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27335O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27335O\"></sup>It opened for them of its own accord, and they went out and went along one street, and immediately the angel left him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When Peter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27336P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27336P\"></sup>came to himself, he said, “Now I am sure that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27336Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27336Q\"></sup>the Lord has sent his angel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27336R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27336R\"></sup>rescued me from the hand of Herod and from all that the Jewish people were expecting.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When he realized this, he went to the house of Mary, the mother of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27337S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27337S\"></sup>John whose other name was Mark, where many were gathered together and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27337T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27337T\"></sup>were praying.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And when he knocked at the door of the gateway, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27338U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27338U\"></sup>a servant girl named Rhoda came to answer.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Recognizing Peter's voice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27339V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27339V\"></sup>in her joy she did not open the gate but ran in and reported that Peter was standing at the gate.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>They said to her, “You are out of your mind.” But she kept insisting that it was so, and they kept saying, “It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27340W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27340W\"></sup>his angel!”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But Peter continued knocking, and when they opened, they saw him and were amazed.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27342X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27342X\"></sup>motioning to them with his hand to be silent, he described to them how the Lord had brought him out of the prison. And he said, “Tell these things to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27342Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27342Y\"></sup>James and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27342Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27342Z\"></sup>the brothers.” Then he departed and went to another place.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now when day came, there was no little disturbance among the soldiers over what had become of Peter.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And after Herod searched for him and did not find him, he examined the sentries and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27344AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27344AA\"></sup>ordered that they should be put to death. Then he went down from Judea to Caesarea and spent time there.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now Herod was angry with the people of Tyre and Sidon, and they came to him with one accord, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27345AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27345AB\"></sup>having persuaded Blastus, the king's chamberlain, they asked for peace, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27345AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27345AC\"></sup>their country depended on the king's country for food.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>On an appointed day Herod put on his royal robes, took his seat upon the throne, and delivered an oration to them.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And the people were shouting, “The voice of a god, and not of a man!”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27348AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27348AD\"></sup>an angel of the Lord struck him down, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27348AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27348AE\"></sup>he did not give God the glory, and he was eaten by worms and breathed his last.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27349AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27349AF\"></sup>the word of God increased and multiplied.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27350AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27350AG\"></sup>And Barnabas and Saul returned from Jerusalem when they had completed their service, bringing with them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27350AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27350AH\"></sup>John, whose other name was Mark."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>Now there were in the church at Antioch <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27351A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27351A\"></sup>prophets and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27351B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27351B\"></sup>teachers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27351C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27351C\"></sup>Barnabas, Simeon who was called Niger, Lucius of Cyrene, Manaen a lifelong friend of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27351D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27351D\"></sup>Herod the tetrarch, and Saul.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>While they were worshiping the Lord and fasting, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27352E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27352E\"></sup>the Holy Spirit said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27352F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27352F\"></sup>“Set apart for me Barnabas and Saul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27352G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27352G\"></sup>for the work to which I have called them.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then after fasting and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27353H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27353H\"></sup>praying they laid their hands on them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27353I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27353I\"></sup>sent them off.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So, being sent out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27354J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27354J\"></sup>by the Holy Spirit, they went down to Seleucia, and from there they sailed to Cyprus.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When they arrived at Salamis, they proclaimed the word of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27355K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27355K\"></sup>in the synagogues of the Jews. And they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27355L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27355L\"></sup>John to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27355M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27355M\"></sup>assist them.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When they had gone through the whole island as far as Paphos, they came upon a certain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27356N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27356N\"></sup>magician, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27356O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27356O\"></sup>a Jewish false prophet named Bar-Jesus.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He was with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27357P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27357P\"></sup>the proconsul, Sergius Paulus, a man of intelligence, who summoned Barnabas and Saul and sought to hear the word of God.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But Elymas the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27358Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27358Q\"></sup>magician (for that is the meaning of his name) <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27358R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27358R\"></sup>opposed them, seeking to turn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27358S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27358S\"></sup>the proconsul away from the faith.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But Saul, who was also called Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27359T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27359T\"></sup>filled with the Holy Spirit, looked intently at him",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and said, “You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27360U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27360U\"></sup>son of the devil, you enemy of all righteousness, full of all deceit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27360V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27360V\"></sup>villainy, will you not stop <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27360W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27360W\"></sup>making crooked <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27360X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27360X\"></sup>the straight paths of the Lord?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And now, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27361Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27361Y\"></sup>the hand of the Lord is upon you, and you will be blind and unable to see the sun for a time.” Immediately mist and darkness fell upon him, and he went about seeking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27361Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27361Z\"></sup>people to lead him by the hand.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the proconsul believed, when he saw what had occurred, for he was astonished at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27362AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27362AA\"></sup>the teaching of the Lord.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now Paul and his companions set sail from Paphos and came to Perga in Pamphylia. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27363AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27363AB\"></sup>John left them and returned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27363AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27363AC\"></sup>to Jerusalem,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>but they went on from Perga and came to Antioch in Pisidia. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27364AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27364AD\"></sup>on the Sabbath day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27364AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27364AE\"></sup>they went into the synagogue and sat down.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>After <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27365AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27365AF\"></sup>the reading from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27365AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27365AG\"></sup>the Law and the Prophets, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27365AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27365AH\"></sup>the rulers of the synagogue sent a message to them, saying, “Brothers, if you have any <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27365AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27365AI\"></sup>word of encouragement for the people, say it.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So Paul stood up, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27366AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27366AJ\"></sup>motioning with his hand said:“Men of Israel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27366AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27366AK\"></sup>you who fear God, listen.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27367AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27367AL\"></sup>The God of this people Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27367AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27367AM\"></sup>chose our fathers and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27367AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27367AN\"></sup>made the people great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27367AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27367AO\"></sup>during their stay in the land of Egypt, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27367AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27367AP\"></sup>with uplifted arm he led them out of it.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And for about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27368AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27368AQ\"></sup>forty years <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27368AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27368AR\"></sup>he put up with them in the wilderness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27369AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27369AS\"></sup>after destroying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27369AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27369AT\"></sup>seven nations in the land of Canaan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27369AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27369AU\"></sup>he gave them their land as an inheritance.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>All this took about 450 years. And after that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27370AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27370AV\"></sup>he gave them judges until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27370AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27370AW\"></sup>Samuel the prophet.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27371AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27371AX\"></sup>they asked for a king, and God gave them Saul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27371AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27371AY\"></sup>the son of Kish, a man of the tribe of Benjamin, for forty years.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27372AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27372AZ\"></sup>when he had removed him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27372BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27372BA\"></sup>he raised up David to be their king, of whom he testified and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27372BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27372BB\"></sup>‘I have found in David the son of Jesse <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27372BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27372BC\"></sup>a man after my heart, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27372BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27372BD\"></sup>who will do all my will.’",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27373BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27373BE\"></sup>Of this man's offspring God has brought to Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27373BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27373BF\"></sup>a Savior, Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27373BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27373BG\"></sup>as he promised.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Before his coming, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27374BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27374BH\"></sup>John had proclaimed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27374BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27374BI\"></sup>a baptism of repentance to all the people of Israel.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And as John was finishing his course, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27375BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27375BJ\"></sup>he said, ‘What do you suppose that I am? I am not he. No, but behold, after me one is coming, the sandals of whose feet I am not worthy to untie.’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Brothers, sons of the family of Abraham, and those among you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27376BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27376BK\"></sup>who fear God, to us has been sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27376BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27376BL\"></sup>the message of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27376BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27376BM\"></sup>this salvation.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For those who live in Jerusalem and their rulers, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27377BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27377BN\"></sup>they did not recognize him nor understand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27377BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27377BO\"></sup>the utterances of the prophets, which are read every Sabbath, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27377BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27377BP\"></sup>fulfilled them by condemning him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27378BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27378BQ\"></sup>though they found in him no guilt worthy of death, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27378BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27378BR\"></sup>they asked Pilate to have him executed.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27379BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27379BS\"></sup>they had carried out all that was written of him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27379BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27379BT\"></sup>they took him down from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27379BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27379BU\"></sup>the tree and laid him in a tomb.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27380BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27380BV\"></sup>God raised him from the dead,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>and for many days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27381BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27381BW\"></sup>he appeared to those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27381BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27381BX\"></sup>who had come up with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27381BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27381BY\"></sup>from Galilee to Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27381BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27381BZ\"></sup>who are now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27381CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27381CA\"></sup>his witnesses to the people.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And we bring you the good news <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27382CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27382CB\"></sup>that what God promised to the fathers,",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27383CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27383CC\"></sup>this he has fulfilled to us their children by raising Jesus, as also it is written in the second Psalm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27383CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27383CD\"></sup>“‘You are my Son,today I have begotten you.’",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And as for the fact that he raised him from the dead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27384CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27384CE\"></sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27384CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27384CF\"></sup>no more to return to corruption, he has spoken in this way,“‘I will give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27384CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27384CG\"></sup>the holy and sure blessings of David.’",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Therefore he says also in another psalm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27385CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27385CH\"></sup>“‘You will not let your Holy One see corruption.’",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>For David, after he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27386CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27386CI\"></sup>served the purpose of God in his own generation, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27386CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27386CJ\"></sup>fell asleep and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27386CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27386CK\"></sup>was laid with his fathers and saw corruption,",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>but he whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27387CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27387CL\"></sup>God raised up did not see corruption.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Let it be known to you therefore, brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27388CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27388CM\"></sup>that through this man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27388CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27388CN\"></sup>forgiveness of sins is proclaimed to you,",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>and by him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27389CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27389CO\"></sup>everyone who believes is freed from everything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27389CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27389CP\"></sup>from which you could not be freed by the law of Moses.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Beware, therefore, lest what is said in the Prophets should come about:",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27391CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27391CQ\"></sup>“‘Look, you scoffers,be astounded and perish;for I am doing a work in your days,a work that you will not believe, even if one tells it to you.’”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>As they went out, the people begged that these things might be told them the next Sabbath.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>And after the meeting of the synagogue broke up, many Jews and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27393CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27393CR\"></sup>devout <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27393CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27393CS\"></sup>converts to Judaism followed Paul and Barnabas, who, as they spoke with them, urged them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27393CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27393CT\"></sup>to continue in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27393CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27393CU\"></sup>the grace of God.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>The next Sabbath almost the whole city gathered to hear the word of the Lord.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27395CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27395CV\"></sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27395CW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CW&quot;&gt;CW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27395CW\"></sup>when the Jews saw the crowds, they were filled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27395CX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CX&quot;&gt;CX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27395CX\"></sup>jealousy and began to contradict what was spoken by Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27395CY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CY&quot;&gt;CY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27395CY\"></sup>reviling him.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>And Paul and Barnabas spoke out boldly, saying, “It was necessary that the word of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27396CZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CZ&quot;&gt;CZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27396CZ\"></sup>be spoken first to you. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27396DA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DA&quot;&gt;DA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27396DA\"></sup>Since you thrust it aside and judge yourselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27396DB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DB&quot;&gt;DB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27396DB\"></sup>unworthy of eternal life, behold, we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27396DC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DC&quot;&gt;DC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27396DC\"></sup>are turning to the Gentiles.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27397DD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DD&quot;&gt;DD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27397DD\"></sup>For so the Lord has commanded us, saying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27397DE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DE&quot;&gt;DE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27397DE\"></sup>“‘I have made you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27397DF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DF&quot;&gt;DF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27397DF\"></sup>a light for the Gentiles,that you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27397DG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DG&quot;&gt;DG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27397DG\"></sup>bring salvation to the ends of the earth.’”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>And when the Gentiles heard this, they began rejoicing and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27398DH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DH&quot;&gt;DH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27398DH\"></sup>glorifying the word of the Lord, and as many as were appointed to eternal life believed.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And the word of the Lord was spreading throughout the whole region.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27400DI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DI&quot;&gt;DI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27400DI\"></sup>But the Jews incited the devout <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27400DJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DJ&quot;&gt;DJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27400DJ\"></sup>women of high standing and the leading men of the city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27400DK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DK&quot;&gt;DK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27400DK\"></sup>stirred up persecution against Paul and Barnabas, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27400DL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DL&quot;&gt;DL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27400DL\"></sup>drove them out of their district.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>But they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27401DM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DM&quot;&gt;DM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27401DM\"></sup>shook off the dust from their feet against them and went to Iconium.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>And the disciples were filled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27402DN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DN&quot;&gt;DN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27402DN\"></sup>with joy and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27402DO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference DO&quot;&gt;DO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27402DO\"></sup>with the Holy Spirit."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Now at Iconium <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27403A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27403A\"></sup>they entered together into the Jewish synagogue and spoke in such a way that a great number of both Jews and Greeks believed.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27404B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27404B\"></sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27404C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27404C\"></sup>unbelieving Jews stirred up the Gentiles and poisoned their minds against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27404D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27404D\"></sup>the brothers.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So they remained for a long time, speaking boldly for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27405E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27405E\"></sup>the Lord, who bore witness to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27405F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27405F\"></sup>the word of his grace, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27405G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27405G\"></sup>granting signs and wonders to be done by their hands.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But the people of the city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27406H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27406H\"></sup>were divided; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27406I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27406I\"></sup>some sided with the Jews and some with the apostles.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When an attempt was made by both Gentiles and Jews, with their rulers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27407J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27407J\"></sup>to mistreat them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27407K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27407K\"></sup>to stone them,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>they learned of it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27408L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27408L\"></sup>fled to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27408M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27408M\"></sup>Lystra and Derbe, cities of Lycaonia, and to the surrounding country,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and there they continued to preach the gospel.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now at Lystra there was a man sitting who could not use his feet. He was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27410N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27410N\"></sup>crippled from birth and had never walked.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He listened to Paul speaking. And Paul, looking intently at him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27411O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27411O\"></sup>seeing that he had faith to be made well,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>said in a loud voice, “Stand upright on your feet.” And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27412P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27412P\"></sup>sprang up and began walking.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And when the crowds saw what Paul had done, they lifted up their voices, saying in Lycaonian, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27413Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27413Q\"></sup>“The gods have come down to us in the likeness of men!”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Barnabas they called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27414R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27414R\"></sup>Zeus, and Paul, Hermes, because he was the chief speaker.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the priest of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27415S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27415S\"></sup>Zeus, whose temple was at the entrance to the city, brought oxen and garlands to the gates and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27415T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27415T\"></sup>wanted to offer sacrifice with the crowds.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But when the apostles Barnabas and Paul heard of it, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27416U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27416U\"></sup>tore their garments and rushed out into the crowd, crying out,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27417V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27417V\"></sup>why are you doing these things? We also are men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27417W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27417W\"></sup>of like nature with you, and we bring you good news, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27417X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27417X\"></sup>you should turn from these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27417Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27417Y\"></sup>vain things to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27417Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27417Z\"></sup>a living God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27417AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27417AA\"></sup>who made the heaven and the earth and the sea and all that is in them.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In past generations he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27418AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27418AB\"></sup>allowed all the nations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27418AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27418AC\"></sup>to walk in their own ways.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27419AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27419AD\"></sup>he did not leave himself without witness, for he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27419AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27419AE\"></sup>did good by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27419AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27419AF\"></sup>giving you rains from heaven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27419AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27419AG\"></sup>fruitful seasons, satisfying your hearts with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27419AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27419AH\"></sup>food and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27419AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27419AI\"></sup>gladness.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Even with these words they scarcely restrained the people from offering sacrifice to them.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27421AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27421AJ\"></sup>But Jews came from Antioch and Iconium, and having persuaded the crowds, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27421AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27421AK\"></sup>they stoned Paul and dragged him out of the city, supposing that he was dead.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But when the disciples gathered about him, he rose up and entered the city, and on the next day he went on with Barnabas to Derbe.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>When they had preached the gospel to that city and had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27423AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27423AL\"></sup>made many disciples, they returned to Lystra and to Iconium and to Antioch,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27424AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27424AM\"></sup>strengthening the souls of the disciples, encouraging them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27424AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27424AN\"></sup>to continue in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27424AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27424AO\"></sup>the faith, and saying that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27424AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27424AP\"></sup>through many tribulations we must enter the kingdom of God.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And when they had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27425AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27425AQ\"></sup>appointed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27425AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27425AR\"></sup>elders for them in every church, with prayer and fasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27425AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27425AS\"></sup>they committed them to the Lord in whom they had believed.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then they passed through Pisidia and came to Pamphylia.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And when they had spoken the word in Perga, they went down to Attalia,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and from there they sailed to Antioch, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27428AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27428AT\"></sup>where they had been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27428AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27428AU\"></sup>commended to the grace of God for the work that they had fulfilled.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And when they arrived and gathered the church together, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27429AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27429AV\"></sup>they declared all that God had done with them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27429AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27429AW\"></sup>how he had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27429AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27429AX\"></sup>opened <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27429AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27429AY\"></sup>a door of faith to the Gentiles.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And they remained no little time with the disciples."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27431A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27431A\"></sup>But some men came down from Judea and were teaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27431B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27431B\"></sup>the brothers, “Unless you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27431C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27431C\"></sup>circumcised <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27431D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27431D\"></sup>according to the custom of Moses, you cannot be saved.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And after Paul and Barnabas had no small dissension and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27432E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27432E\"></sup>debate with them, Paul and Barnabas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27432F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27432F\"></sup>some of the others were appointed to go up to Jerusalem to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27432G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27432G\"></sup>the apostles and the elders about this question.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27433H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27433H\"></sup>being sent on their way by the church, they passed through both Phoenicia and Samaria, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27433I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27433I\"></sup>describing in detail the conversion of the Gentiles, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27433J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27433J\"></sup>brought great joy to all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27433K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27433K\"></sup>the brothers.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27434L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27434L\"></sup>When they came to Jerusalem, they were welcomed by the church and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27434M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27434M\"></sup>the apostles and the elders, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27434N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27434N\"></sup>they declared all that God had done with them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But some believers who belonged to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27435O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27435O\"></sup>the party of the Pharisees rose up and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27435P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27435P\"></sup>“It is necessary <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27435Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27435Q\"></sup>to circumcise them and to order them to keep the law of Moses.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27436R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27436R\"></sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27436S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27436S\"></sup>apostles and the elders were gathered together to consider this matter.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And after there had been much <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27437T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27437T\"></sup>debate, Peter stood up and said to them, “Brothers, you know that in the early days God made a choice among you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27437U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27437U\"></sup>that by my mouth the Gentiles should hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27437V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27437V\"></sup>the word of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27437W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27437W\"></sup>the gospel and believe.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27438X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27438X\"></sup>who knows the heart, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27438Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27438Y\"></sup>bore witness to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27438Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27438Z\"></sup>by giving them the Holy Spirit just as he did to us,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27439AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27439AA\"></sup>he made no distinction between us and them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27439AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27439AB\"></sup>having cleansed their hearts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27439AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27439AC\"></sup>by faith.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now, therefore, why <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27440AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27440AD\"></sup>are you putting God to the test <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27440AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27440AE\"></sup>by placing a yoke on the neck of the disciples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27440AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27440AF\"></sup>that neither our fathers nor we have been able to bear?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27441AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27441AG\"></sup>believe that we will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27441AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27441AH\"></sup>saved through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27441AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27441AI\"></sup>the grace of the Lord Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27441AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27441AJ\"></sup>just as they will.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And all the assembly fell silent, and they listened to Barnabas and Paul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27442AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27442AK\"></sup>as they related what signs and wonders God had done through them among the Gentiles.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>After they finished speaking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27443AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27443AL\"></sup>James replied, “Brothers, listen to me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27444AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27444AM\"></sup>Simeon has related how God first visited the Gentiles, to take from them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27444AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27444AN\"></sup>a people for his name.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And with this the words of the prophets agree, just as it is written,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27446AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27446AO\"></sup>“‘After this I will return,and I will rebuild the tent of David that has fallen;I will rebuild its ruins, and I will restore it,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>that the remnant of mankind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27447AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27447AP\"></sup>may seek the Lord,and all the Gentiles <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27447AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27447AQ\"></sup>who are called by my name, says the Lord, who makes these things",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27448AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27448AR\"></sup>known from of old.’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27449AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27449AS\"></sup>my judgment is that we should not trouble those of the Gentiles who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27449AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27449AT\"></sup>turn to God,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>but should write to them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27450AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27450AU\"></sup>to abstain from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27450AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27450AV\"></sup>the things polluted by idols, and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27450AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27450AW\"></sup>sexual immorality, and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27450AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27450AX\"></sup>what has been strangled, and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27450AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27450AY\"></sup>blood.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For from ancient generations Moses has had in every city those who proclaim him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27451AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27451AZ\"></sup>for he is read every Sabbath in the synagogues.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then it seemed good to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27452BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27452BA\"></sup>the apostles and the elders, with the whole church, to choose men from among them and send them to Antioch with Paul and Barnabas. They sent Judas called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27452BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27452BB\"></sup>Barsabbas, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27452BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27452BC\"></sup>Silas, leading men among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27452BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27452BD\"></sup>the brothers,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>with the following letter: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27453BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27453BE\"></sup>“The brothers, both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27453BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27453BF\"></sup>the apostles and the elders, to the brothers who are of the Gentiles in Antioch and Syria and Cilicia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27453BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27453BG\"></sup>greetings.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Since we have heard that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27454BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27454BH\"></sup>some persons have gone out from us and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27454BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27454BI\"></sup>troubled you with words, unsettling your minds, although we gave them no instructions,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>it has seemed good to us, having come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27455BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27455BJ\"></sup>to one accord, to choose men and send them to you with our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27455BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27455BK\"></sup>beloved Barnabas and Paul,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27456BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27456BL\"></sup>men who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27456BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27456BM\"></sup>risked their lives for the name of our Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>We have therefore sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27457BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27457BN\"></sup>Judas and Silas, who themselves will tell you the same things by word of mouth.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>For it has seemed good <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27458BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27458BO\"></sup>to the Holy Spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27458BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27458BP\"></sup>to us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27458BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27458BQ\"></sup>to lay on you no greater burden than these requirements:",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27459BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27459BR\"></sup>that you abstain from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27459BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27459BS\"></sup>what has been sacrificed to idols, and from blood, and from what has been strangled, and from sexual immorality. If you keep yourselves from these, you will do well. Farewell.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>So when they were sent off, they went down to Antioch, and having gathered the congregation together, they delivered the letter.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And when they had read it, they rejoiced because of its encouragement.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And Judas and Silas, who were themselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27462BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27462BT\"></sup>prophets, encouraged and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27462BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27462BU\"></sup>strengthened <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27462BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27462BV\"></sup>the brothers with many words.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And after they had spent some time, they were sent off <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27463BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27463BW\"></sup>in peace by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27463BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27463BX\"></sup>the brothers to those who had sent them.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27464BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27464BY\"></sup>Paul and Barnabas remained in Antioch, teaching and preaching the word of the Lord, with many others also.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And after some days Paul said to Barnabas, “Let us return and visit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27465BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27465BZ\"></sup>the brothers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27465CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27465CA\"></sup>in every city where we proclaimed the word of the Lord, and see how they are.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Now Barnabas wanted to take with them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27466CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27466CB\"></sup>John called Mark.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But Paul thought best not to take with them one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27467CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27467CC\"></sup>who had withdrawn from them in Pamphylia and had not gone with them to the work.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And there arose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27468CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27468CD\"></sup>a sharp disagreement, so that they separated from each other. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27468CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27468CE\"></sup>Barnabas took Mark with him and sailed away to Cyprus,",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>but Paul chose Silas and departed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27469CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27469CF\"></sup>having been commended by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27469CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27469CG\"></sup>the brothers to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27469CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27469CH\"></sup>the grace of the Lord.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And he went through Syria and Cilicia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27470CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27470CI\"></sup>strengthening the churches."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Paul came also to Derbe and to Lystra. A disciple was there, named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27471A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27471A\"></sup>Timothy, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27471B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27471B\"></sup>the son of a Jewish woman who was a believer, but his father was a Greek.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He was well spoken of by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27472C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27472C\"></sup>the brothers at Lystra and Iconium.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Paul wanted Timothy to accompany him, and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27473D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27473D\"></sup>took him and circumcised him because of the Jews who were in those places, for they all knew that his father was a Greek.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>As they went on their way through the cities, they delivered to them for observance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27474E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27474E\"></sup>the decisions <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27474F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27474F\"></sup>that had been reached by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27474G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27474G\"></sup>the apostles and elders who were in Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27475H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27475H\"></sup>So the churches were strengthened in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27475I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27475I\"></sup>the faith, and they increased in numbers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27475J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27475J\"></sup>daily.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27476K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27476K\"></sup>they went through the region of Phrygia and Galatia, having been forbidden by the Holy Spirit to speak the word in Asia.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And when they had come up to Mysia, they attempted to go into Bithynia, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27477L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27477L\"></sup>the Spirit of Jesus did not allow them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So, passing by Mysia, they went down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27478M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27478M\"></sup>to Troas.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And a vision appeared to Paul in the night: a man of Macedonia was standing there, urging him and saying, “Come over to Macedonia and help us.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And when Paul had seen the vision, immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27480N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27480N\"></sup>we sought to go on into Macedonia, concluding that God had called us to preach the gospel to them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So, setting sail from Troas, we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27481O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27481O\"></sup>made a direct voyage to Samothrace, and the following day to Neapolis,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and from there to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27482P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27482P\"></sup>Philippi, which is a leading city of the district of Macedonia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27482Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27482Q\"></sup>a Roman colony. We remained in this city some days.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27483R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27483R\"></sup>on the Sabbath day we went outside the gate <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27483S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27483S\"></sup>to the riverside, where we supposed there was a place of prayer, and we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27483T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27483T\"></sup>sat down and spoke to the women who had come together.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>One who heard us was a woman named Lydia, from the city of Thyatira, a seller of purple goods, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27484U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27484U\"></sup>who was a worshiper of God. The Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27484V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27484V\"></sup>opened her heart to pay attention to what was said by Paul.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And after she was baptized, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27485W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27485W\"></sup>and her household as well, she urged us, saying, “If you have judged me to be faithful to the Lord, come to my house and stay.” And she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27485X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27485X\"></sup>prevailed upon us.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>As we were going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27486Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27486Y\"></sup>the place of prayer, we were met by a slave girl who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27486Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27486Z\"></sup>a spirit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27486AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27486AA\"></sup>divination and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27486AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27486AB\"></sup>brought her owners much gain by fortune-telling.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>She followed Paul and us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27487AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27487AC\"></sup>crying out, “These men are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27487AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27487AD\"></sup>servants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27487AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27487AE\"></sup>the Most High God, who proclaim to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27487AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27487AF\"></sup>the way of salvation.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And this she kept doing for many days. Paul, having become greatly annoyed, turned and said to the spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27488AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27488AG\"></sup>“I command you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27488AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27488AH\"></sup>in the name of Jesus Christ to come out of her.” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27488AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27488AI\"></sup>it came out that very hour.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27489AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27489AJ\"></sup>when her owners saw that their hope of gain was gone, they seized Paul and Silas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27489AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27489AK\"></sup>dragged them into the marketplace before the rulers.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And when they had brought them to the magistrates, they said, “These men are Jews, and they are disturbing our city.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27491AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27491AL\"></sup>advocate customs that are not lawful for us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27491AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27491AM\"></sup>as Romans to accept or practice.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The crowd joined in attacking them, and the magistrates tore the garments off them and gave orders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27492AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27492AN\"></sup>to beat them with rods.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And when they had inflicted many blows upon them, they threw them into prison, ordering the jailer to keep them safely.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Having received this order, he put them into the inner <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27494AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27494AO\"></sup>prison and fastened their feet in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27494AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27494AP\"></sup>the stocks.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27495AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27495AQ\"></sup>About midnight Paul and Silas were praying and singing hymns to God, and the prisoners were listening to them,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>and suddenly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27496AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27496AR\"></sup>there was a great earthquake, so that the foundations of the prison were shaken. And immediately <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27496AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27496AS\"></sup>all the doors were opened, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27496AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27496AT\"></sup>everyone's bonds were unfastened.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When the jailer woke and saw that the prison doors were open, he drew his sword and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27497AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27497AU\"></sup>was about to kill himself, supposing that the prisoners had escaped.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But Paul cried with a loud voice, “Do not harm yourself, for we are all here.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And the jailer called for lights and rushed in, and trembling with fear he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27499AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27499AV\"></sup>fell down before Paul and Silas.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then he brought them out and said, “Sirs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27500AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27500AW\"></sup>what must I do to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27500AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27500AX\"></sup>saved?”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And they said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27501AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27501AY\"></sup>“Believe in the Lord Jesus, and you will be saved, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27501AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27501AZ\"></sup>and your household.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And they spoke the word of the Lord to him and to all who were in his house.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And he took them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27503BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27503BA\"></sup>the same hour of the night and washed their wounds; and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27503BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27503BB\"></sup>was baptized at once, he and all his family.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Then he brought them up into his house and set food before them. And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27504BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27504BC\"></sup>rejoiced along with his entire household that he had believed in God.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>But when it was day, the magistrates sent the police, saying, “Let those men go.”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And the jailer reported these words to Paul, saying, “The magistrates have sent to let you go. Therefore come out now and go in peace.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But Paul said to them, “They have beaten us publicly, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27507BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27507BD\"></sup>uncondemned, men who are Roman citizens, and have thrown us into prison; and do they now throw us out secretly? No! Let them come themselves and take us out.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>The police reported these words to the magistrates, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27508BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27508BE\"></sup>they were afraid when they heard that they were Roman citizens.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>So they came and apologized to them. And they took them out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27509BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27509BF\"></sup>asked them to leave the city.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>So they went out of the prison and visited <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27510BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27510BG\"></sup>Lydia. And when they had seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27510BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27510BH\"></sup>the brothers, they encouraged them and departed."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>Now when they had passed through Amphipolis and Apollonia, they came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27511A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27511A\"></sup>Thessalonica, where there was a synagogue of the Jews.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And Paul went in, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27512B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27512B\"></sup>as was his custom, and on three Sabbath days he reasoned with them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27512C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27512C\"></sup>from the Scriptures,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27513D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27513D\"></sup>explaining and proving that it was necessary for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27513E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27513E\"></sup>the Christ to suffer and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27513F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27513F\"></sup>to rise from the dead, and saying, “This Jesus, whom I proclaim to you, is the Christ.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27514G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27514G\"></sup>some of them were persuaded and joined Paul and Silas, as did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27514H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27514H\"></sup>a great many of the devout <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27514I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27514I\"></sup>Greeks and not a few of the leading women.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27515J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27515J\"></sup>But the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27515K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27515K\"></sup>were jealous, and taking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27515L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27515L\"></sup>some wicked men of the rabble, they formed a mob, set the city in an uproar, and attacked the house of Jason, seeking to bring them out to the crowd.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And when they could not find them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27516M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27516M\"></sup>they dragged Jason and some of the brothers before the city authorities, shouting, “These men who have turned the world upside down have come here also,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and Jason has received them, and they are all acting against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27517N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27517N\"></sup>the decrees of Caesar, saying that there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27517O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27517O\"></sup>another king, Jesus.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the people and the city authorities were disturbed when they heard these things.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And when they had taken money as security from Jason and the rest, they let them go.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27520P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27520P\"></sup>The brothers immediately sent Paul and Silas away by night to Berea, and when they arrived they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27520Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27520Q\"></sup>went into the Jewish synagogue.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now these Jews were more noble than those in Thessalonica; they received the word with all eagerness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27521R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27521R\"></sup>examining the Scriptures daily to see if these things were so.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27522S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27522S\"></sup>Many of them therefore believed, with not a few Greek <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27522T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27522T\"></sup>women of high standing as well as men.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But when the Jews from Thessalonica learned that the word of God was proclaimed by Paul at Berea also, they came there too, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27523U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27523U\"></sup>agitating and stirring up the crowds.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the brothers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27524V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27524V\"></sup>immediately sent Paul off on his way to the sea, but Silas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27524W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27524W\"></sup>Timothy remained there.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27525X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27525X\"></sup>Those who conducted Paul brought him as far as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27525Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27525Y\"></sup>Athens, and after receiving a command <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27525Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27525Z\"></sup>for Silas and Timothy to come to him as soon as possible, they departed.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now while Paul was waiting for them at Athens, his spirit was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27526AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27526AA\"></sup>provoked within him as he saw that the city was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27526AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27526AB\"></sup>full of idols.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27527AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27527AC\"></sup>he reasoned in the synagogue with the Jews and the devout persons, and in the marketplace every day with those who happened to be there.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Some of the Epicurean and Stoic philosophers also conversed with him. And some said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27528AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27528AD\"></sup>“What does this babbler wish to say?” Others said, “He seems to be a preacher of foreign divinities”—because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27528AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27528AE\"></sup>he was preaching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27528AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27528AF\"></sup>Jesus and the resurrection.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And they took him and brought him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27529AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27529AG\"></sup>the Areopagus, saying, “May we know what this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27529AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27529AH\"></sup>new teaching is that you are presenting?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For you bring some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27530AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27530AI\"></sup>strange things to our ears. We wish to know therefore what these things mean.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Now all the Athenians and the foreigners who lived there would spend their time in nothing except telling or hearing something new.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So Paul, standing in the midst of the Areopagus, said: “Men of Athens, I perceive that in every way you are very religious.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For as I passed along and observed the objects of your worship, I found also an altar with this inscription: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27533AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27533AJ\"></sup>‘To the unknown god.’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27533AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27533AK\"></sup>What therefore you worship <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27533AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27533AL\"></sup>as unknown, this I proclaim to you.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27534AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27534AM\"></sup>The God who made the world and everything in it, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27534AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27534AN\"></sup>Lord of heaven and earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27534AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27534AO\"></sup>does not live in temples made by man,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>nor is he served by human hands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27535AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27535AP\"></sup>as though he needed anything, since he himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27535AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27535AQ\"></sup>gives to all mankind <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27535AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27535AR\"></sup>life and breath and everything.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27536AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27536AS\"></sup>he made from one man every nation of mankind to live <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27536AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27536AT\"></sup>on all the face of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27536AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27536AU\"></sup>having determined allotted periods and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27536AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27536AV\"></sup>the boundaries of their dwelling place,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27537AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27537AW\"></sup>that they should seek God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27537AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27537AX\"></sup>and perhaps feel their way toward him and find him. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27537AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27537AY\"></sup>Yet he is actually not far from each one of us,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>for<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27538AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27538AZ\"></sup>“‘In him we live and move and have our being’;as even some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27538BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27538BA\"></sup>your own poets have said,“‘For we are indeed his offspring.’",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27539BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27539BB\"></sup>Being then God's offspring, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27539BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27539BC\"></sup>we ought not to think that the divine being is like gold or silver or stone, an image formed by the art and imagination of man.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27540BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27540BD\"></sup>The times of ignorance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27540BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27540BE\"></sup>God overlooked, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27540BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27540BF\"></sup>now he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27540BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27540BG\"></sup>commands all people everywhere to repent,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>because he has fixed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27541BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27541BH\"></sup>a day on which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27541BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27541BI\"></sup>he will judge the world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27541BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27541BJ\"></sup>in righteousness by a man whom he has appointed; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27541BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27541BK\"></sup>of this he has given assurance to all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27541BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27541BL\"></sup>by raising him from the dead.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Now when they heard of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27542BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27542BM\"></sup>the resurrection of the dead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27542BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27542BN\"></sup>some mocked. But others said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27542BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27542BO\"></sup>“We will hear you again about this.”",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So Paul went out from their midst.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But some men joined him and believed, among whom also were Dionysius <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27544BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27544BP\"></sup>the Areopagite and a woman named Damaris and others with them."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>After this Paul left Athens and went to Corinth.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he found a Jew named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27546A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27546A\"></sup>Aquila, a native of Pontus, recently come from Italy with his wife <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27546B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27546B\"></sup>Priscilla, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27546C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27546C\"></sup>Claudius had commanded all the Jews to leave Rome. And he went to see them,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27547D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27547D\"></sup>because he was of the same trade he stayed with them and worked, for they were tentmakers by trade.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27548E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27548E\"></sup>he reasoned in the synagogue <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27548F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27548F\"></sup>every Sabbath, and tried to persuade Jews and Greeks.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27549G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27549G\"></sup>When Silas and Timothy arrived from Macedonia, Paul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27549H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27549H\"></sup>was occupied with the word, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27549I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27549I\"></sup>testifying to the Jews that the Christ was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27549J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27549J\"></sup>Jesus.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And when they opposed and reviled him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27550K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27550K\"></sup>he shook out his garments and said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27550L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27550L\"></sup>“Your blood be on your own heads! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27550M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27550M\"></sup>I am innocent. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27550N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27550N\"></sup>From now on I will go to the Gentiles.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he left there and went to the house of a man named Titius <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27551O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27551O\"></sup>Justus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27551P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27551P\"></sup>a worshiper of God. His house was next door to the synagogue.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27552Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27552Q\"></sup>Crispus, the ruler of the synagogue, believed in the Lord, together <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27552R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27552R\"></sup>with his entire household. And many of the Corinthians hearing Paul believed and were baptized.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the Lord said to Paul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27553S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27553S\"></sup>one night in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27553T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27553T\"></sup>a vision, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27553U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27553U\"></sup>“Do not be afraid, but go on speaking and do not be silent,</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27554V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27554V\"></sup>for I am with you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27554W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27554W\"></sup>no one will attack you to harm you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27554X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27554X\"></sup>I have many in this city who are my people.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he stayed a year and six months, teaching the word of God among them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But when Gallio was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27556Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27556Y\"></sup>proconsul of Achaia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27556Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27556Z\"></sup>the Jews made a united attack on Paul and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27556AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27556AA\"></sup>brought him before the tribunal,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>saying, “This man is persuading people to worship God contrary to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27557AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27557AB\"></sup>the law.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But when Paul was about to open his mouth, Gallio said to the Jews, “If it were a matter of wrongdoing or vicious <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27558AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27558AC\"></sup>crime, O Jews, I would have reason to accept your complaint.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27559AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27559AD\"></sup>since it is a matter of questions about words and names and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27559AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27559AE\"></sup>your own law, see to it yourselves. I refuse to be a judge of these things.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And he drove them from the tribunal.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And they all seized Sosthenes, the ruler of the synagogue, and beat him in front of the tribunal. But Gallio paid no attention to any of this.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>After this, Paul stayed many days longer and then took leave of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27562AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27562AF\"></sup>the brothers and set sail for Syria, and with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27562AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27562AG\"></sup>Priscilla and Aquila. At <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27562AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27562AH\"></sup>Cenchreae <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27562AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27562AI\"></sup>he had cut his hair, for he was under a vow.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And they came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27563AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27563AJ\"></sup>Ephesus, and he left them there, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27563AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27563AK\"></sup>he himself went into the synagogue and reasoned with the Jews.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When they asked him to stay for a longer period, he declined.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But on taking leave of them he said, “I will return to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27565AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27565AL\"></sup>if God wills,” and he set sail from Ephesus.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>When he had landed at Caesarea, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27566AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27566AM\"></sup>went up and greeted the church, and then went down to Antioch.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>After spending some time there, he departed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27567AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27567AN\"></sup>went from one place to the next through the region of Galatia and Phrygia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27567AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27567AO\"></sup>strengthening all the disciples.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now a Jew named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27568AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27568AP\"></sup>Apollos, a native of Alexandria, came to Ephesus. He was an eloquent man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27568AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27568AQ\"></sup>competent in the Scriptures.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He had been instructed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27569AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27569AR\"></sup>the way of the Lord. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27569AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27569AS\"></sup>being fervent in spirit, he spoke and taught accurately the things concerning Jesus, though he knew only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27569AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27569AT\"></sup>the baptism of John.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He began to speak boldly in the synagogue, but when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27570AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27570AU\"></sup>Priscilla and Aquila heard him, they took him aside and explained to him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27570AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27570AV\"></sup>the way of God more accurately.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And when he wished to cross to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27571AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27571AW\"></sup>Achaia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27571AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27571AX\"></sup>the brothers encouraged him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27571AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27571AY\"></sup>wrote to the disciples to welcome him. When he arrived, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27571AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27571AZ\"></sup>he greatly helped those who through grace had believed,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>for he powerfully refuted the Jews in public, showing by the Scriptures <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27572BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27572BA\"></sup>that the Christ was Jesus."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>And it happened that while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27573A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27573A\"></sup>Apollos was at Corinth, Paul passed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27573B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27573B\"></sup>through the inland country and came to Ephesus. There he found some disciples.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he said to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27574C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27574C\"></sup>“Did you receive the Holy Spirit when you believed?” And they said, “No, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27574D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27574D\"></sup>we have not even heard that there is a Holy Spirit.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27575E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27575E\"></sup>“Into what then were you baptized?” They said, “Into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27575F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27575F\"></sup>John's baptism.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Paul said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27576G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27576G\"></sup>“John baptized with the baptism of repentance, telling the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27576H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27576H\"></sup>to believe in the one who was to come after him, that is, Jesus.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>On hearing this, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27577I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27577I\"></sup>they were baptized in the name of the Lord Jesus.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27578J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27578J\"></sup>when Paul had laid his hands on them, the Holy Spirit came on them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27578K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27578K\"></sup>they began speaking in tongues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27578L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27578L\"></sup>prophesying.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There were about twelve men in all.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27580M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27580M\"></sup>he entered the synagogue and for three months spoke boldly, reasoning and persuading them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27580N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27580N\"></sup>about the kingdom of God.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27581O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27581O\"></sup>But when some became stubborn and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27581P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27581P\"></sup>continued in unbelief, speaking evil of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27581Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27581Q\"></sup>the Way before the congregation, he withdrew from them and took the disciples with him, reasoning daily in the hall of Tyrannus.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This continued for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27582R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27582R\"></sup>two years, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27582S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27582S\"></sup>all the residents of Asia heard the word of the Lord, both Jews and Greeks.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27583T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27583T\"></sup>God was doing extraordinary miracles by the hands of Paul,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27584U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27584U\"></sup>so that even handkerchiefs or aprons that had touched his skin were carried away to the sick, and their diseases left them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27584V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27584V\"></sup>the evil spirits came out of them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then some of the itinerant Jewish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27585W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27585W\"></sup>exorcists <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27585X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27585X\"></sup>undertook to invoke the name of the Lord Jesus over those who had evil spirits, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27585Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27585Y\"></sup>“I adjure you by the Jesus whom Paul proclaims.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Seven sons of a Jewish high priest named Sceva were doing this.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But the evil spirit answered them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27587Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27587Z\"></sup>“Jesus I know, and Paul I recognize, but who are you?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the man in whom was the evil spirit leaped on them, mastered all of them and overpowered them, so that they fled out of that house naked and wounded.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And this became known to all the residents of Ephesus, both Jews and Greeks. And fear fell upon them all, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27589AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27589AA\"></sup>the name of the Lord Jesus was extolled.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Also many of those who were now believers came, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27590AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27590AB\"></sup>confessing and divulging their practices.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And a number of those who had practiced magic arts brought their books together and burned them in the sight of all. And they counted the value of them and found it came to fifty thousand pieces of silver.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So the word of the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27592AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27592AC\"></sup>continued to increase and prevail mightily.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Now after these events Paul resolved in the Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27593AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27593AD\"></sup>to pass through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27593AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27593AE\"></sup>Macedonia and Achaia and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27593AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27593AF\"></sup>go to Jerusalem, saying, “After I have been there, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27593AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27593AG\"></sup>I must also see Rome.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And having sent into Macedonia two of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27594AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27594AH\"></sup>his helpers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27594AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27594AI\"></sup>Timothy and Erastus, he himself stayed in Asia <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27594AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27594AJ\"></sup>for a while.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>About that time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27595AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27595AK\"></sup>there arose no little disturbance concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27595AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27595AL\"></sup>the Way.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For a man named Demetrius, a silversmith, who made silver shrines of Artemis, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27596AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27596AM\"></sup>brought no little business to the craftsmen.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27597AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27597AN\"></sup>These he gathered together, with the workmen in similar trades, and said, “Men, you know that from this business we have our wealth.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And you see and hear that not only in Ephesus but in almost all of Asia this Paul has persuaded and turned away a great many people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27598AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27598AO\"></sup>saying that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27598AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27598AP\"></sup>gods made with hands are not gods.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And there is danger not only that this trade of ours may come into disrepute but also that the temple of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27599AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27599AQ\"></sup>great goddess Artemis may be counted as nothing, and that she may even be deposed from her magnificence, she whom all Asia and the world worship.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When they heard this they were enraged and were crying out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27600AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27600AR\"></sup>“Great is Artemis of the Ephesians!”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So the city was filled with the confusion, and they rushed together into the theater, dragging with them Gaius and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27601AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27601AS\"></sup>Aristarchus, Macedonians who were Paul's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27601AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27601AT\"></sup>companions in travel.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But when Paul wished to go in among the crowd, the disciples would not let him.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And even some of the Asiarchs, who were friends of his, sent to him and were urging him not to venture into the theater.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27604AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27604AU\"></sup>Now some cried out one thing, some another, for the assembly was in confusion, and most of them did not know why they had come together.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Some of the crowd prompted Alexander, whom the Jews had put forward. And Alexander, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27605AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27605AV\"></sup>motioning with his hand, wanted to make a defense to the crowd.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But when they recognized that he was a Jew, for about two hours they all cried out with one voice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27606AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27606AW\"></sup>“Great is Artemis of the Ephesians!”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And when the town clerk had quieted the crowd, he said, “Men of Ephesus, who is there who does not know that the city of the Ephesians is temple keeper of the great Artemis, and of the sacred stone that fell from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27607AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27607AX\"></sup>the sky?",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Seeing then that these things cannot be denied, you ought to be quiet and do nothing rash.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For you have brought <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27609AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27609AY\"></sup>these men here who are neither <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27609AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27609AZ\"></sup>sacrilegious nor blasphemers of our goddess.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>If therefore Demetrius and the craftsmen with him have a complaint against anyone, the courts are open, and there are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27610BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27610BA\"></sup>proconsuls. Let them bring charges against one another.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But if you seek anything further, it shall be settled in the regular assembly.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>For we really are in danger of being charged with rioting today, since there is no cause that we can give to justify this commotion.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>And when he had said these things, he dismissed the assembly."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>After the uproar ceased, Paul sent for the disciples, and after encouraging them, he said farewell and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27614A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27614A\"></sup>departed for Macedonia.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When he had gone through those regions and had given them much encouragement, he came to Greece.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>There he spent three months, and when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27616B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27616B\"></sup>a plot was made against him by the Jews as he was about to set sail for Syria, he decided to return through Macedonia.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Sopater the Berean, son of Pyrrhus, accompanied him; and of the Thessalonians, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27617C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27617C\"></sup>Aristarchus and Secundus; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27617D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27617D\"></sup>Gaius of Derbe, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27617E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27617E\"></sup>Timothy; and the Asians, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27617F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27617F\"></sup>Tychicus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27617G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27617G\"></sup>Trophimus.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>These went on ahead and were waiting for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27618H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27618H\"></sup>us at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27618I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27618I\"></sup>Troas,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but we sailed away from Philippi after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27619J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27619J\"></sup>the days of Unleavened Bread, and in five days we came to them at Troas, where we stayed for seven days.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27620K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27620K\"></sup>On the first day of the week, when we were gathered together <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27620L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27620L\"></sup>to break bread, Paul talked with them, intending to depart on the next day, and he prolonged his speech until midnight.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>There were many lamps in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27621M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27621M\"></sup>the upper room where we were gathered.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And a young man named Eutychus, sitting at the window, sank into a deep sleep as Paul talked still longer. And being overcome by sleep, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27622N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27622N\"></sup>fell down from the third story and was taken up dead.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But Paul went down and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27623O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27623O\"></sup>bent over him, and taking him in his arms, said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27623P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27623P\"></sup>“Do not be alarmed, for his life is in him.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And when Paul had gone up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27624Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27624Q\"></sup>had broken bread and eaten, he conversed with them a long while, until daybreak, and so departed.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And they took the youth away alive, and were not a little comforted.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But going ahead to the ship, we set sail for Assos, intending to take Paul aboard there, for so he had arranged, intending himself to go by land.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And when he met us at Assos, we took him on board and went to Mitylene.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And sailing from there we came the following day opposite Chios; the next day we touched at Samos; and the day after that we went to Miletus.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For Paul had decided to sail past Ephesus, so that he might not have to spend time in Asia, for he was hastening <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27629R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27629R\"></sup>to be at Jerusalem, if possible, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27629S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27629S\"></sup>on the day of Pentecost.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now from Miletus he sent to Ephesus and called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27630T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27630T\"></sup>the elders of the church to come to him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And when they came to him, he said to them:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27631U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27631U\"></sup>“You yourselves know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27631V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27631V\"></sup>how I lived among you the whole time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27631W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27631W\"></sup>from the first day that I set foot in Asia,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27632X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27632X\"></sup>serving the Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27632Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27632Y\"></sup>with all humility and with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27632Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27632Z\"></sup>tears and with trials that happened to me through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27632AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27632AA\"></sup>the plots of the Jews;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>how I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27633AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27633AB\"></sup>did not shrink from declaring to you anything that was profitable, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27633AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27633AC\"></sup>teaching you in public and from house to house,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27634AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27634AD\"></sup>testifying both to Jews and to Greeks of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27634AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27634AE\"></sup>repentance toward God and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27634AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27634AF\"></sup>faith in our Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And now, behold, I am going to Jerusalem, constrained <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27635AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27635AG\"></sup>by the Spirit, not knowing what will happen to me there,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>except that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27636AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27636AH\"></sup>the Holy Spirit testifies to me in every city that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27636AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27636AI\"></sup>imprisonment and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27636AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27636AJ\"></sup>afflictions await me.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27637AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27637AK\"></sup>I do not account my life of any value nor as precious to myself, if only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27637AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27637AL\"></sup>I may finish my course and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27637AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27637AM\"></sup>the ministry <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27637AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27637AN\"></sup>that I received from the Lord Jesus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27637AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27637AO\"></sup>to testify to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27637AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27637AP\"></sup>the gospel of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27637AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27637AQ\"></sup>the grace of God.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And now, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27638AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27638AR\"></sup>I know that none of you among whom I have gone about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27638AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27638AS\"></sup>proclaiming the kingdom will see my face again.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27639AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27639AT\"></sup>I testify to you this day that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27639AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27639AU\"></sup>I am innocent of the blood of all,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27640AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27640AV\"></sup>I did not shrink from declaring to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27640AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27640AW\"></sup>the whole counsel of God.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27641AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27641AX\"></sup>Pay careful attention to yourselves and to all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27641AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27641AY\"></sup>the flock, in which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27641AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27641AZ\"></sup>the Holy Spirit has made you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27641BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27641BA\"></sup>overseers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27641BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27641BB\"></sup>to care for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27641BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27641BC\"></sup>the church of God, which he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27641BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27641BD\"></sup>obtained <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27641BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27641BE\"></sup>with his own blood.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27642BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27642BF\"></sup>know that after my departure <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27642BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27642BG\"></sup>fierce wolves will come in among you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27642BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27642BH\"></sup>not sparing the flock;",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27643BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27643BI\"></sup>from among your own selves will arise men speaking twisted things, to draw away the disciples after them.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27644BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27644BJ\"></sup>be alert, remembering that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27644BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27644BK\"></sup>for three years I did not cease night or day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27644BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27644BL\"></sup>to admonish every one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27644BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27644BM\"></sup>with tears.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27645BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27645BN\"></sup>I commend you to God and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27645BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27645BO\"></sup>the word of his grace, which is able to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27645BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27645BP\"></sup>build you up and to give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27645BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27645BQ\"></sup>the inheritance among all those who are sanctified.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27646BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27646BR\"></sup>I coveted no one's silver or gold or apparel.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27647BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27647BS\"></sup>You yourselves know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27647BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27647BT\"></sup>these hands ministered to my necessities and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27647BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27647BU\"></sup>to those who were with me.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>In all things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27648BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27648BV\"></sup>I have shown you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27648BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27648BW\"></sup>by working hard in this way we must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27648BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27648BX\"></sup>help the weak and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27648BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27648BY\"></sup>remember the words of the Lord Jesus, how he himself said, <span class=\"woj\">‘It is more blessed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27648BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27648BZ\"></sup>to give than to receive.’</span>”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And when he had said these things, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27649CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27649CA\"></sup>he knelt down and prayed with them all.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27650CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27650CB\"></sup>there was much weeping on the part of all; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27650CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27650CC\"></sup>they embraced Paul and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27650CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27650CD\"></sup>kissed him,",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>being sorrowful most of all because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27651CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27651CE\"></sup>the word he had spoken, that they would not see his face again. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27651CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27651CF\"></sup>they accompanied him to the ship."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>And when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27652A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27652A\"></sup>we had parted from them and set sail, we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27652B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27652B\"></sup>came by a straight course to Cos, and the next day to Rhodes, and from there to Patara.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And having found a ship crossing to Phoenicia, we went aboard and set sail.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When we had come in sight of Cyprus, leaving it on the left we sailed to Syria and landed at Tyre, for there the ship was to unload its cargo.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And having sought out the disciples, we stayed there for seven days. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27655C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27655C\"></sup>through the Spirit they were telling Paul not to go on to Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When our days there were ended, we departed and went on our journey, and they all, with wives and children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27656D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27656D\"></sup>accompanied us until we were outside the city. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27656E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27656E\"></sup>kneeling down on the beach, we prayed",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and said farewell to one another. Then we went on board the ship, and they returned home.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When we had finished the voyage from Tyre, we arrived at Ptolemais, and we greeted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27658F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27658F\"></sup>the brothers and stayed with them for one day.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>On the next day we departed and came to Caesarea, and we entered the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27659G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27659G\"></sup>Philip <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27659H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27659H\"></sup>the evangelist, who was one of the seven, and stayed with him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He had four unmarried daughters, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27660I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27660I\"></sup>who prophesied.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>While we were staying for many days, a prophet named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27661J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27661J\"></sup>Agabus came down from Judea.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And coming to us, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27662K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27662K\"></sup>took Paul's belt and bound his own feet and hands and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27662L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27662L\"></sup>“Thus says the Holy Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27662M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27662M\"></sup>‘This is how the Jews at Jerusalem will bind the man who owns this belt and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27662N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27662N\"></sup>deliver him into the hands of the Gentiles.’”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When we heard this, we and the people there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27663O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27663O\"></sup>urged him not to go up to Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then Paul answered, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27664P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27664P\"></sup>“What are you doing, weeping and breaking my heart? For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27664Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27664Q\"></sup>I am ready not only to be imprisoned but even to die in Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27664R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27664R\"></sup>for the name of the Lord Jesus.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And since he would not be persuaded, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27665S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27665S\"></sup>we ceased and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27665T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27665T\"></sup>“Let the will of the Lord be done.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>After these days we got ready and went up to Jerusalem.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And some of the disciples from Caesarea went with us, bringing us to the house of Mnason of Cyprus, an early disciple, with whom we should lodge.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>When we had come to Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27668U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27668U\"></sup>the brothers received us gladly.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>On the following day Paul went in with us to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27669V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27669V\"></sup>James, and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27669W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27669W\"></sup>the elders were present.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>After greeting them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27670X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27670X\"></sup>he related one by one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27670Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27670Y\"></sup>the things that God had done among the Gentiles through his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27670Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27670Z\"></sup>ministry.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And when they heard it, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27671AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27671AA\"></sup>glorified God. And they said to him, “You see, brother, how many thousands there are among the Jews of those who have believed. They are all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27671AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27671AB\"></sup>zealous for the law,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>and they have been told about you that you teach all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27672AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27672AC\"></sup>the Jews who are among the Gentiles to forsake Moses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27672AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27672AD\"></sup>telling them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27672AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27672AE\"></sup>not to circumcise their children or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27672AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27672AF\"></sup>walk according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27672AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27672AG\"></sup>our customs.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>What then is to be done? They will certainly hear that you have come.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Do therefore what we tell you. We have four men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27674AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27674AH\"></sup>who are under a vow;",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>take these men and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27675AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27675AI\"></sup>purify yourself along with them and pay their expenses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27675AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27675AJ\"></sup>so that they may shave their heads. Thus all will know that there is nothing in what they have been told about you, but that you yourself also live in observance of the law.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But as for the Gentiles who have believed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27676AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27676AK\"></sup>we have sent a letter with our judgment that they should abstain from what has been sacrificed to idols, and from blood, and from what has been strangled, and from sexual immorality.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then Paul took the men, and the next day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27677AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27677AL\"></sup>he purified himself along with them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27677AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27677AM\"></sup>went into the temple, giving notice when the days of purification would be fulfilled and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27677AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27677AN\"></sup>the offering presented for each one of them.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27678AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27678AO\"></sup>the seven days were almost completed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27678AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27678AP\"></sup>the Jews from Asia, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27678AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27678AQ\"></sup>seeing him in the temple, stirred up the whole crowd and laid hands on him,",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>crying out, “Men of Israel, help! This is the man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27679AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27679AR\"></sup>is teaching everyone everywhere against the people and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27679AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27679AS\"></sup>the law and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27679AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27679AT\"></sup>this place. Moreover, he even brought Greeks into the temple and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27679AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27679AU\"></sup>has defiled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27679AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27679AV\"></sup>this holy place.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For they had previously seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27680AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27680AW\"></sup>Trophimus the Ephesian with him in the city, and they supposed that Paul had brought him into the temple.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then all the city was stirred up, and the people ran together. They seized Paul and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27681AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27681AX\"></sup>dragged him out of the temple, and at once the gates were shut.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27682AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27682AY\"></sup>And as they were seeking to kill him, word came to the tribune of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27682AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27682AZ\"></sup>the cohort that all Jerusalem was in confusion.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27683BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27683BA\"></sup>He at once took soldiers and centurions and ran down to them. And when they saw the tribune and the soldiers, they stopped beating Paul.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Then the tribune came up and arrested him and ordered him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27684BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27684BB\"></sup>to be bound <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27684BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27684BC\"></sup>with two chains. He inquired who he was and what he had done.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27685BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27685BD\"></sup>Some in the crowd were shouting one thing, some another. And as he could not learn the facts because of the uproar, he ordered him to be brought into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27685BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27685BE\"></sup>the barracks.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And when he came to the steps, he was actually carried by the soldiers because of the violence of the crowd,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>for the mob of the people followed, crying out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27687BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27687BF\"></sup>“Away with him!”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>As Paul was about to be brought into the barracks, he said to the tribune, “May I say something to you?” And he said, “Do you know Greek?",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Are you not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27689BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27689BG\"></sup>the Egyptian, then, who recently stirred up a revolt and led the four thousand men of the Assassins out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27689BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27689BH\"></sup>into the wilderness?”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Paul replied, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27690BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27690BI\"></sup>“I am a Jew, from Tarsus in Cilicia, a citizen of no obscure city. I beg you, permit me to speak to the people.”",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And when he had given him permission, Paul, standing on the steps, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27691BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27691BJ\"></sup>motioned with his hand to the people. And when there was a great hush, he addressed them in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27691BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27691BK\"></sup>the Hebrew language, saying:"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27692A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27692A\"></sup>“Brothers and fathers, hear the defense that I now make before you.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And when they heard that he was addressing them in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27693B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27693B\"></sup>the Hebrew language, they became even more quiet. And he said:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27694C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27694C\"></sup>“I am a Jew, born in Tarsus in Cilicia, but brought up in this city, educated <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27694D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27694D\"></sup>at the feet of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27694E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27694E\"></sup>Gamaliel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27694F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27694F\"></sup>according to the strict manner of the law of our fathers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27694G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27694G\"></sup>being zealous for God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27694H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27694H\"></sup>as all of you are this day.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27695I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27695I\"></sup>I persecuted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27695J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27695J\"></sup>this Way <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27695K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27695K\"></sup>to the death, binding and delivering to prison both men and women,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27696L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27696L\"></sup>the high priest and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27696M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27696M\"></sup>the whole council of elders can bear me witness. From them I received letters to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27696N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27696N\"></sup>the brothers, and I journeyed toward Damascus to take those also who were there and bring them in bonds to Jerusalem to be punished.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27697O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27697O\"></sup>“As I was on my way and drew near to Damascus, about noon a great light from heaven suddenly shone around me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And I fell to the ground and heard a voice saying to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Saul, Saul, why are you persecuting me?’</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And I answered, ‘Who are you, Lord?’ And he said to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27699P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27699P\"></sup>Jesus of Nazareth, whom you are persecuting.’</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27700Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27700Q\"></sup>Now those who were with me saw the light but did not understand the voice of the one who was speaking to me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And I said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27701R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27701R\"></sup>‘What shall I do, Lord?’ And the Lord said to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Rise, and go into Damascus, and there you will be told all that is appointed for you to do.’</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And since I could not see because of the brightness of that light, I was led by the hand by those who were with me, and came into Damascus.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27703S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27703S\"></sup>one Ananias, a devout man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27703T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27703T\"></sup>according to the law, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27703U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27703U\"></sup>well spoken of by all the Jews who lived there,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27704V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27704V\"></sup>came to me, and standing by me said to me, ‘Brother Saul, receive your sight.’ And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27704W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27704W\"></sup>at that very hour I received my sight and saw him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27705X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27705X\"></sup>‘The God of our fathers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27705Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27705Y\"></sup>appointed you to know his will, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27705Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27705Z\"></sup>to see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27705AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27705AA\"></sup>the Righteous One and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27705AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27705AB\"></sup>to hear a voice from his mouth;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27706AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27706AC\"></sup>you will be a witness for him to everyone of what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27706AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27706AD\"></sup>you have seen and heard.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And now why do you wait? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27707AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27707AE\"></sup>Rise and be baptized and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27707AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27707AF\"></sup>wash away your sins, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27707AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27707AG\"></sup>calling on his name.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27708AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27708AH\"></sup>“When I had returned to Jerusalem and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27708AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27708AI\"></sup>was praying in the temple, I fell into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27708AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27708AJ\"></sup>a trance",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and saw him saying to me, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27709AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27709AK\"></sup>‘Make haste and get out of Jerusalem quickly, because they will not accept your testimony about me.’</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I said, ‘Lord, they themselves know that in one synagogue after another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27710AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27710AL\"></sup>I imprisoned and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27710AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27710AM\"></sup>beat those who believed in you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And when the blood of Stephen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27711AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27711AN\"></sup>your witness was being shed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27711AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27711AO\"></sup>I myself was standing by and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27711AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27711AP\"></sup>approving and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27711AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27711AQ\"></sup>watching over the garments of those who killed him.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And he said to me, <span class=\"woj\">‘Go, for I will send you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27712AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27712AR\"></sup>far away to the Gentiles.’</span>”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Up to this word they listened to him. Then they raised their voices and said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27713AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27713AS\"></sup>“Away with such a fellow from the earth! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27713AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27713AT\"></sup>he should not be allowed to live.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And as they were shouting and throwing off their cloaks and flinging dust into the air,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>the tribune ordered him to be brought into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27715AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27715AU\"></sup>the barracks, saying that he should be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27715AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27715AV\"></sup>examined by flogging, to find out why they were shouting against him like this.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But when they had stretched him out for the whips, Paul said to the centurion who was standing by, “Is it lawful for you to flog <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27716AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27716AW\"></sup>a man who is a Roman citizen and uncondemned?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>When the centurion heard this, he went to the tribune and said to him, “What are you about to do? For this man is a Roman citizen.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>So the tribune came and said to him, “Tell me, are you a Roman citizen?” And he said, “Yes.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>The tribune answered, “I bought this citizenship for a large sum.” Paul said, “But I am a citizen by birth.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So those who were about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27720AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27720AX\"></sup>to examine him withdrew from him immediately, and the tribune also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27720AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27720AY\"></sup>was afraid, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27720AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27720AZ\"></sup>for he realized that Paul was a Roman citizen and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27720BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27720BA\"></sup>he had bound him.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But on the next day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27721BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27721BB\"></sup>desiring to know the real reason why he was being accused by the Jews, he unbound him and commanded the chief priests and all the council to meet, and he brought Paul down and set him before them."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>And looking intently at the council, Paul said, “Brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27722A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27722A\"></sup>I have lived my life before God in all good conscience up to this day.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27723B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27723B\"></sup>Ananias commanded those who stood by him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27723C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27723C\"></sup>to strike him on the mouth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then Paul said to him, “God is going to strike you, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27724D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27724D\"></sup>whitewashed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27724E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27724E\"></sup>wall! Are you sitting to judge me according to the law, and yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27724F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27724F\"></sup>contrary to the law you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27724G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27724G\"></sup>order me to be struck?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Those who stood by said, “Would you revile <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27725H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27725H\"></sup>God's high priest?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And Paul said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27726I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27726I\"></sup>“I did not know, brothers, that he was the high priest, for it is written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27726J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27726J\"></sup>‘You shall not speak evil of a ruler of your people.’”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now when Paul perceived that one part were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27727K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27727K\"></sup>Sadducees and the other Pharisees, he cried out in the council, “Brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27727L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27727L\"></sup>I am a Pharisee, a son of Pharisees. It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27727M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27727M\"></sup>with respect to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27727N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27727N\"></sup>hope and the resurrection of the dead that I am on trial.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And when he had said this, a dissension arose between the Pharisees and the Sadducees, and the assembly was divided.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the Sadducees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27729O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27729O\"></sup>say that there is no resurrection, nor angel, nor spirit, but the Pharisees acknowledge them all.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then a great clamor arose, and some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27730P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27730P\"></sup>the scribes of the Pharisees' party stood up and contended sharply, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27730Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27730Q\"></sup>“We find nothing wrong in this man. What <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27730R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27730R\"></sup>if a spirit or an angel spoke to him?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And when the dissension became violent, the tribune, afraid that Paul would be torn to pieces by them, commanded the soldiers to go down and take him away from among them by force and bring him into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27731S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27731S\"></sup>the barracks.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27732T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27732T\"></sup>The following night <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27732U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27732U\"></sup>the Lord stood by him and said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27732V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27732V\"></sup>“Take courage, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27732W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27732W\"></sup>as you have testified to the facts about me in Jerusalem, so you must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27732X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27732X\"></sup>testify also in Rome.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When it was day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27733Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27733Y\"></sup>the Jews made a plot and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27733Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27733Z\"></sup>bound themselves by an oath neither to eat nor drink till they had killed Paul.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>There were more than forty who made this conspiracy.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They went to the chief priests and elders and said, “We have strictly bound ourselves by an oath to taste no food till we have killed Paul.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now therefore you, along with the council, give notice to the tribune to bring him down to you, as though you were going to determine his case more exactly. And we are ready to kill him before he comes near.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Now the son of Paul's sister heard of their ambush, so he went and entered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27737AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27737AA\"></sup>the barracks and told Paul.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Paul called one of the centurions and said, “Take this young man to the tribune, for he has something to tell him.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>So he took him and brought him to the tribune and said, “Paul <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27739AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27739AB\"></sup>the prisoner called me and asked me to bring this young man to you, as he has something to say to you.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The tribune took him by the hand, and going aside asked him privately, “What is it that you have to tell me?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And he said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27741AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27741AC\"></sup>“The Jews have agreed to ask you to bring Paul down to the council tomorrow, as though they were going to inquire somewhat more closely about him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But do not be persuaded by them, for more than forty of their men are lying in ambush for him, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27742AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27742AD\"></sup>have bound themselves by an oath neither to eat nor drink till they have killed him. And now they are ready, waiting for your consent.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>So the tribune dismissed the young man, charging him, “Tell no one that you have informed me of these things.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then he called two of the centurions and said, “Get ready two hundred soldiers, with seventy horsemen and two hundred spearmen to go as far as Caesarea at the third hour of the night.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Also provide mounts for Paul to ride and bring him safely to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27745AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27745AE\"></sup>Felix <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27745AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27745AF\"></sup>the governor.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And he wrote a letter to this effect:",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Claudius Lysias, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27747AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27747AG\"></sup>his Excellency the governor Felix, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27747AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27747AH\"></sup>greetings.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27748AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27748AI\"></sup>This man was seized by the Jews and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27748AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27748AJ\"></sup>was about to be killed by them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27748AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27748AK\"></sup>when I came upon them with the soldiers and rescued him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27748AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27748AL\"></sup>having learned that he was a Roman citizen.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27749AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27749AM\"></sup>desiring to know the charge for which they were accusing him, I brought him down to their council.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I found that he was being accused <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27750AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27750AN\"></sup>about questions of their law, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27750AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27750AO\"></sup>charged with nothing deserving death or imprisonment.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27751AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27751AP\"></sup>And when it was disclosed to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27751AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27751AQ\"></sup>that there would be a plot against the man, I sent him to you at once, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27751AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27751AR\"></sup>ordering his accusers also to state before you what they have against him.”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So the soldiers, according to their instructions, took Paul and brought him by night to Antipatris.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And on the next day they returned to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27753AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27753AS\"></sup>the barracks, letting the horsemen go on with him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>When they had come to Caesarea and delivered the letter to the governor, they presented Paul also before him.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>On reading the letter, he asked what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27755AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27755AT\"></sup>province he was from. And when he learned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27755AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27755AU\"></sup>that he was from Cilicia,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>he said, “I will give you a hearing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27756AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27756AV\"></sup>when your accusers arrive.” And he commanded him to be guarded in Herod's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27756AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27756AW\"></sup>praetorium."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27757A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27757A\"></sup>after five days the high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27757B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27757B\"></sup>Ananias came down with some elders and a spokesman, one Tertullus. They laid before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27757C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27757C\"></sup>the governor their case against Paul.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And when he had been summoned, Tertullus began to accuse him, saying:“Since through you we enjoy much peace, and since by your foresight, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27758D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27758D\"></sup>most excellent Felix, reforms are being made for this nation,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>in every way and everywhere we accept this with all gratitude.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But, to detain you no further, I beg you in your kindness to hear us briefly.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For we have found this man a plague, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27761E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27761E\"></sup>one who stirs up riots among all the Jews throughout the world and is a ringleader of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27761F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27761F\"></sup>the sect of the Nazarenes.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27762G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27762G\"></sup>He even tried to profane the temple, but we seized him.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>By examining him yourself you will be able to find out from him about everything of which we accuse him.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The Jews also joined in the charge, affirming that all these things were so.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And when the governor had nodded to him to speak, Paul replied:“Knowing that for many years you have been a judge over this nation, I cheerfully make my defense.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>You can verify that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27766H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27766H\"></sup>it is not more than twelve days since I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27766I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27766I\"></sup>went up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27766J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27766J\"></sup>to worship in Jerusalem,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27767K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27767K\"></sup>they did not find me disputing with anyone or stirring up a crowd, either in the temple or in the synagogues or in the city.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27768L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27768L\"></sup>Neither can they prove to you what they now bring up against me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But this I confess to you, that according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27769M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27769M\"></sup>the Way, which they call <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27769N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27769N\"></sup>a sect, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27769O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27769O\"></sup>I worship <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27769P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27769P\"></sup>the God of our fathers, believing everything <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27769Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27769Q\"></sup>laid down by the Law and written in the Prophets,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27770R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27770R\"></sup>having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27770S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27770S\"></sup>a hope in God, which these men themselves accept, that there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27770T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27770T\"></sup>a resurrection <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27770U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27770U\"></sup>of both the just and the unjust.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So I always <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27771V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27771V\"></sup>take pains to have a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27771W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27771W\"></sup>clear conscience toward both God and man.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27772X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27772X\"></sup>after several years <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27772Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27772Y\"></sup>I came to bring alms to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27772Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27772Z\"></sup>my nation and to present <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27772AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27772AA\"></sup>offerings.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>While I was doing this, they found me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27773AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27773AB\"></sup>purified in the temple, without any crowd or tumult. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27773AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27773AC\"></sup>some Jews from Asia—",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27774AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27774AD\"></sup>they ought to be here before you and to make an accusation, should they have anything against me.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Or else let these men themselves say what wrongdoing they found when I stood before the council,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>other than this one thing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27776AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27776AE\"></sup>that I cried out while standing among them: ‘It is with respect to the resurrection of the dead that I am on trial before you this day.’”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But Felix, having a rather accurate knowledge of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27777AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27777AF\"></sup>the Way, put them off, saying, “When Lysias the tribune comes down, I will decide your case.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then he gave orders to the centurion that he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27778AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27778AG\"></sup>should be kept in custody but have some liberty, and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27778AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27778AH\"></sup>none of his friends should be prevented from attending to his needs.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>After some days Felix came with his wife Drusilla, who was Jewish, and he sent for Paul and heard him speak about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27779AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27779AI\"></sup>faith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27779AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27779AJ\"></sup>in Christ Jesus.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And as he reasoned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27780AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27780AK\"></sup>about righteousness and self-control and the coming judgment, Felix was alarmed and said, “Go away for the present. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27780AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27780AL\"></sup>When I get an opportunity I will summon you.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>At the same time he hoped <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27781AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27781AM\"></sup>that money would be given him by Paul. So he sent for him often and conversed with him.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When two years had elapsed, Felix was succeeded by Porcius <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27782AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27782AN\"></sup>Festus. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27782AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27782AO\"></sup>desiring to do the Jews a favor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27782AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27782AP\"></sup>Felix left Paul in prison."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>Now three days after Festus had arrived in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27783A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27783A\"></sup>the province, he went up to Jerusalem from Caesarea.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the chief priests and the principal men of the Jews <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27784B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27784B\"></sup>laid out their case against Paul, and they urged him,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>asking as a favor against Paul that he summon him to Jerusalem—because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27785C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27785C\"></sup>they were planning an ambush to kill him on the way.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Festus replied that Paul was being kept at Caesarea and that he himself intended to go there shortly.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“So,” said he, “let the men of authority among you go down with me, and if there is anything wrong about the man, let them bring charges against him.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>After he stayed among them not more than eight or ten days, he went down to Caesarea. And the next day he took his seat on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27788D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27788D\"></sup>the tribunal and ordered Paul to be brought.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When he had arrived, the Jews who had come down from Jerusalem stood around him, bringing many and serious charges against him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27789E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27789E\"></sup>that they could not prove.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Paul argued in his defense, “Neither <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27790F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27790F\"></sup>against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27790G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27790G\"></sup>the law of the Jews, nor against the temple, nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27790H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27790H\"></sup>against Caesar have I committed any offense.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But Festus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27791I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27791I\"></sup>wishing to do the Jews a favor, said to Paul, “Do you wish to go up to Jerusalem and there be tried on these charges before me?”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But Paul said, “I am standing before Caesar's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27792J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27792J\"></sup>tribunal, where I ought to be tried. To the Jews I have done no wrong, as you yourself know very well.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If then I am a wrongdoer and have committed anything for which I deserve to die, I do not seek to escape death. But if there is nothing to their charges against me, no one can give me up to them. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27793K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27793K\"></sup>I appeal to Caesar.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then Festus, when he had conferred with his council, answered, “To Caesar you have appealed; to Caesar you shall go.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now when some days had passed, Agrippa the king and Bernice arrived at Caesarea and greeted Festus.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And as they stayed there many days, Festus laid Paul's case before the king, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27796L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27796L\"></sup>“There is a man left prisoner by Felix,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and when I was at Jerusalem, the chief priests and the elders of the Jews laid out their case <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27797M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27797M\"></sup>against him, asking for a sentence of condemnation against him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27798N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27798N\"></sup>I answered them that it was not the custom of the Romans to give up anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27798O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27798O\"></sup>before the accused met the accusers face to face and had opportunity to make his defense concerning the charge laid against him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27799P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27799P\"></sup>So when they came together here, I made no delay, but on the next day took my seat on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27799Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27799Q\"></sup>the tribunal and ordered the man to be brought.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When the accusers stood up, they brought no charge in his case of such evils as I supposed.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Rather they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27801R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27801R\"></sup>had certain points of dispute with him about their own religion and about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27801S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27801S\"></sup>a certain Jesus, who was dead, but whom Paul asserted to be alive.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Being at a loss how to investigate these questions, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27802T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27802T\"></sup>asked whether he wanted to go to Jerusalem and be tried there regarding them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27803U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27803U\"></sup>when Paul had appealed to be kept in custody for the decision of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27803V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27803V\"></sup>the emperor, I ordered him to be held until I could send him to Caesar.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27804W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27804W\"></sup>Agrippa said to Festus, “I would like to hear the man myself.” “Tomorrow,” said he, “you will hear him.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>So on the next day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27805X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27805X\"></sup>Agrippa and Bernice came with great pomp, and they entered the audience hall with the military tribunes and the prominent men of the city. Then, at the command of Festus, Paul was brought in.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And Festus said, “King Agrippa and all who are present with us, you see this man about whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27806Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27806Y\"></sup>the whole Jewish people petitioned me, both in Jerusalem and here, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27806Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27806Z\"></sup>shouting that he ought not to live any longer.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But I found that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27807AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27807AA\"></sup>he had done nothing deserving death. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27807AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27807AB\"></sup>as he himself appealed to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27807AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27807AC\"></sup>the emperor, I decided to go ahead and send him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But I have nothing definite to write to my lord about him. Therefore I have brought him before you all, and especially before you, King Agrippa, so that, after we have examined him, I may have something to write.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For it seems to me unreasonable, in sending a prisoner, not to indicate the charges against him.”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27810A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27810A\"></sup>Agrippa said to Paul, “You have permission to speak for yourself.” Then Paul stretched out his hand and made his defense:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I consider myself fortunate that it is before you, King Agrippa, I am going to make my defense today <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27811B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27811B\"></sup>against all the accusations of the Jews,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>especially because you are familiar with all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27812C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27812C\"></sup>customs and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27812D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27812D\"></sup>controversies of the Jews. Therefore I beg you to listen to me patiently.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27813E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27813E\"></sup>“My manner of life from my youth, spent from the beginning among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27813F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27813F\"></sup>my own nation and in Jerusalem, is known by all the Jews.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They have known for a long time, if they are willing to testify, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27814G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27814G\"></sup>according to the strictest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27814H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27814H\"></sup>party of our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27814I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27814I\"></sup>religion I have lived as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27814J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27814J\"></sup>a Pharisee.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And now I stand here on trial because of my hope in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27815K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27815K\"></sup>the promise made by God to our fathers,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27816L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27816L\"></sup>to which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27816M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27816M\"></sup>our twelve tribes hope to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27816N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27816N\"></sup>attain, as they earnestly worship night and day. And for this hope <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27816O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27816O\"></sup>I am accused by Jews, O king!",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Why is it thought <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27817P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27817P\"></sup>incredible by any of you that God raises the dead?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27818Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27818Q\"></sup>“I myself was convinced that I ought to do many things in opposing the name of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27818R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27818R\"></sup>Jesus of Nazareth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27819S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27819S\"></sup>And I did so in Jerusalem. I not only locked up many of the saints in prison after receiving authority <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27819T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27819T\"></sup>from the chief priests, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27819U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27819U\"></sup>when they were put to death I cast my vote against them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27820V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27820V\"></sup>I punished them often in all the synagogues and tried to make them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27820W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27820W\"></sup>blaspheme, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27820X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27820X\"></sup>in raging fury against them I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27820Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27820Y\"></sup>persecuted them even to foreign cities.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“In this connection <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27821Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27821Z\"></sup>I journeyed to Damascus with the authority and commission of the chief priests.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>At midday, O king, I saw on the way a light from heaven, brighter than the sun, that shone around me and those who journeyed with me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And when we had all fallen to the ground, I heard a voice saying to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27823AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27823AA\"></sup>in the Hebrew language, <span class=\"woj\">‘Saul, Saul, why are you persecuting me? It is hard for you to kick against the goads.’</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And I said, ‘Who are you, Lord?’ And the Lord said, <span class=\"woj\">‘I am Jesus whom you are persecuting.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But rise and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27825AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27825AB\"></sup>stand upon your feet, for I have appeared to you for this purpose, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27825AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27825AC\"></sup>to appoint you as a servant and witness to the things in which you have seen me and to those in which I will appear to you,</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27826AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27826AD\"></sup>delivering you from your people and from the Gentiles—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27826AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27826AE\"></sup>to whom I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27826AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27826AF\"></sup>am sending you</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27827AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27827AG\"></sup>to open their eyes, so that they may turn from darkness to light and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27827AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27827AH\"></sup>the power of Satan to God, that they may receive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27827AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27827AI\"></sup>forgiveness of sins and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27827AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27827AJ\"></sup>a place among those who are sanctified <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27827AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27827AK\"></sup>by faith in me.’</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Therefore, O King Agrippa, I was not disobedient to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27828AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27828AL\"></sup>the heavenly vision,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>but declared first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27829AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27829AM\"></sup>to those in Damascus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27829AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27829AN\"></sup>then in Jerusalem and throughout all the region of Judea, and also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27829AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27829AO\"></sup>to the Gentiles, that they should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27829AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27829AP\"></sup>repent and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27829AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27829AQ\"></sup>turn to God, performing deeds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27829AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27829AR\"></sup>in keeping with their repentance.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For this reason <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27830AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27830AS\"></sup>the Jews seized me in the temple and tried to kill me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27831AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27831AT\"></sup>To this day I have had the help that comes from God, and so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27831AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27831AU\"></sup>I stand here testifying both to small and great, saying nothing but what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27831AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27831AV\"></sup>the prophets and Moses said would come to pass:",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27832AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27832AW\"></sup>that the Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27832AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27832AX\"></sup>must suffer and that, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27832AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27832AY\"></sup>by being the first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27832AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27832AZ\"></sup>to rise from the dead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27832BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27832BA\"></sup>he would proclaim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27832BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27832BB\"></sup>light both to our people and to the Gentiles.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And as he was saying these things in his defense, Festus said with a loud voice, “Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27833BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27833BC\"></sup>you are out of your mind; your great learning is driving you out of your mind.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But Paul said, “I am not out of my mind, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27834BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27834BD\"></sup>most excellent Festus, but I am speaking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27834BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27834BE\"></sup>true and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27834BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27834BF\"></sup>rational words.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27835BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27835BG\"></sup>the king knows about these things, and to him I speak boldly. For I am persuaded that none of these things has escaped his notice, for this has not been done in a corner.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>King Agrippa, do you believe the prophets? I know that you believe.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And Agrippa said to Paul, “In a short time would you persuade me to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27837BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27837BH\"></sup>a Christian?”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And Paul said, “Whether short or long, I would to God that not only you but also all who hear me this day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27838BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27838BI\"></sup>might become such as I am—except for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27838BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27838BJ\"></sup>these chains.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Then the king rose, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27839BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27839BK\"></sup>the governor and Bernice and those who were sitting with them.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And when they had withdrawn, they said to one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27840BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27840BL\"></sup>“This man is doing nothing to deserve death or imprisonment.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And Agrippa said to Festus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27841BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27841BM\"></sup>“This man could have been set <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27841BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27841BN\"></sup>free if he had not appealed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27841BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27841BO\"></sup>to Caesar.”"
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>And when it was decided <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27842A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27842A\"></sup>that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27842B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27842B\"></sup>we should sail for Italy, they delivered Paul and some other prisoners to a centurion of the Augustan <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27842C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27842C\"></sup>Cohort named Julius.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And embarking in a ship of Adramyttium, which was about to sail to the ports along the coast of Asia, we put to sea, accompanied by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27843D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27843D\"></sup>Aristarchus, a Macedonian from Thessalonica.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The next day we put in at Sidon. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27844E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27844E\"></sup>Julius <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27844F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27844F\"></sup>treated Paul kindly and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27844G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27844G\"></sup>gave him leave to go to his friends and be cared for.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And putting out to sea from there we sailed under the lee of Cyprus, because the winds were against us.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And when we had sailed across the open sea along the coast of Cilicia and Pamphylia, we came to Myra in Lycia.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>There the centurion found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27847H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27847H\"></sup>a ship of Alexandria sailing for Italy and put us on board.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>We sailed slowly for a number of days and arrived with difficulty off Cnidus, and as the wind did not allow us to go farther, we sailed under the lee of Crete off Salmone.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Coasting along it with difficulty, we came to a place called Fair Havens, near which was the city of Lasea.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Since much time had passed, and the voyage was now dangerous because even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27850I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27850I\"></sup>the Fast was already over, Paul advised them,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>saying, “Sirs, I perceive that the voyage will be with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27851J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27851J\"></sup>injury and much loss, not only of the cargo and the ship, but also of our lives.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But the centurion paid more attention to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27852K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27852K\"></sup>the pilot and to the owner of the ship than to what Paul said.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And because the harbor was not suitable to spend the winter in, the majority decided to put out to sea from there, on the chance that somehow they could reach Phoenix, a harbor of Crete, facing both southwest and northwest, and spend the winter there.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now when the south wind blew gently, supposing that they had obtained their purpose, they weighed anchor and sailed along Crete, close to the shore.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But soon a tempestuous wind, called the northeaster, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27855L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27855L\"></sup>struck down from the land.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And when the ship was caught and could not face the wind, we gave way to it and were driven along.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Running under the lee of a small island called Cauda, we managed with difficulty to secure the ship's boat.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>After hoisting it up, they used supports to undergird the ship. Then, fearing that they would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27858M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27858M\"></sup>run aground on the Syrtis, they lowered the gear, and thus they were driven along.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Since we were violently storm-tossed, they began the next day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27859N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27859N\"></sup>to jettison the cargo.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And on the third day they threw the ship's tackle overboard with their own hands.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>When neither sun nor stars appeared for many days, and no small tempest lay on us, all hope of our being saved was at last abandoned.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Since they had been without food for a long time, Paul stood up among them and said, “Men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27862O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27862O\"></sup>you should have listened to me and not have set sail from Crete and incurred this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27862P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27862P\"></sup>injury and loss.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Yet now I urge you to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27863Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27863Q\"></sup>take heart, for there will be no loss of life among you, but only of the ship.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For this very night <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27864R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27864R\"></sup>there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27864S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27864S\"></sup>stood before me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27864T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27864T\"></sup>an angel of the God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27864U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27864U\"></sup>to whom I belong and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27864V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27864V\"></sup>whom I worship,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and he said, ‘Do not be afraid, Paul; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27865W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27865W\"></sup>you must stand before Caesar. And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27865X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27865X\"></sup>God has granted you all those who sail with you.’",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So take heart, men, for I have faith in God that it will be exactly as I have been told.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27867Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27867Y\"></sup>we must <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27867Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27867Z\"></sup>run aground on some island.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>When the fourteenth night had come, as we were being driven across the Adriatic Sea, about midnight the sailors suspected that they were nearing land.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So they took a sounding and found twenty fathoms. A little farther on they took a sounding again and found fifteen fathoms.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And fearing that we might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27870AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27870AA\"></sup>run on the rocks, they let down four anchors from the stern and prayed for day to come.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And as the sailors were seeking to escape from the ship, and had lowered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27871AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27871AB\"></sup>the ship's boat into the sea under pretense of laying out anchors from the bow,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Paul said to the centurion and the soldiers, “Unless these men stay in the ship, you cannot be saved.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Then the soldiers cut away the ropes of the ship's boat and let it go.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>As day was about to dawn, Paul urged them all to take some food, saying, “Today is the fourteenth day that you have continued in suspense and without food, having taken nothing.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Therefore I urge you to take some food. For it will give you strength, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27875AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27875AC\"></sup>not a hair is to perish from the head of any of you.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And when he had said these things, he took bread, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27876AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27876AD\"></sup>giving thanks to God in the presence of all he broke it and began to eat.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Then they all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27877AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27877AE\"></sup>were encouraged and ate some food themselves.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>(We were in all 276 <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27878AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27878AF\"></sup>persons in the ship.)",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And when they had eaten enough, they lightened the ship, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27879AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27879AG\"></sup>throwing out the wheat into the sea.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Now when it was day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27880AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27880AH\"></sup>they did not recognize the land, but they noticed a bay with a beach, on which they planned if possible to run the ship ashore.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>So they cast off the anchors and left them in the sea, at the same time loosening the ropes that tied the rudders. Then hoisting the foresail to the wind they made for the beach.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>But striking a reef, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27882AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27882AI\"></sup>they ran the vessel aground. The bow stuck and remained immovable, and the stern was being broken up by the surf.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27883AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27883AJ\"></sup>The soldiers' plan was to kill the prisoners, lest any should swim away and escape.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>But the centurion, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27884AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27884AK\"></sup>wishing to save Paul, kept them from carrying out their plan. He ordered those who could swim to jump overboard first and make for the land,",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>and the rest on planks or on pieces of the ship. And so it was that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27885AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27885AL\"></sup>all were brought safely to land."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>After we were brought safely through, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27886A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27886A\"></sup>we then learned that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27886B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27886B\"></sup>the island was called Malta.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27887C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27887C\"></sup>The native people showed us unusual <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27887D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27887D\"></sup>kindness, for they kindled a fire and welcomed us all, because it had begun to rain and was cold.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When Paul had gathered a bundle of sticks and put them on the fire, a viper came out because of the heat and fastened on his hand.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27889E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27889E\"></sup>the native people saw the creature hanging from his hand, they said to one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27889F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27889F\"></sup>“No doubt this man is a murderer. Though he has escaped from the sea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27889G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27889G\"></sup>Justice has not allowed him to live.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He, however, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27890H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27890H\"></sup>shook off the creature into the fire and suffered no harm.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They were waiting for him to swell up or suddenly fall down dead. But when they had waited a long time and saw no misfortune come to him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27891I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27891I\"></sup>they changed their minds and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27891J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27891J\"></sup>said that he was a god.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now in the neighborhood of that place were lands belonging to the chief man of the island, named Publius, who received us and entertained us hospitably for three days.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>It happened that the father of Publius lay sick with fever and dysentery. And Paul visited him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27893K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27893K\"></sup>prayed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27893L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27893L\"></sup>putting his hands on him, healed him.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And when this had taken place, the rest of the people on the island who had diseases also came and were cured.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They also honored us greatly, and when we were about to sail, they put on board whatever we needed.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>After three months we set sail in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27896M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27896M\"></sup>a ship that had wintered in the island, a ship of Alexandria, with the twin gods as a figurehead.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Putting in at Syracuse, we stayed there for three days.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And from there we made a circuit and arrived at Rhegium. And after one day a south wind sprang up, and on the second day we came to Puteoli.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>There we found <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27899N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27899N\"></sup>brothers and were invited to stay with them for seven days. And so we came to Rome.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27900O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27900O\"></sup>the brothers there, when they heard about us, came as far as the Forum of Appius and Three Taverns to meet us. On seeing them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27900P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27900P\"></sup>Paul thanked God and took courage.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And when we came into Rome, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27901Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27901Q\"></sup>Paul was allowed to stay by himself, with the soldier who guarded him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>After three days he called together the local leaders of the Jews, and when they had gathered, he said to them, “Brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27902R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27902R\"></sup>though I had done nothing against our people or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27902S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27902S\"></sup>the customs of our fathers, yet I was delivered as a prisoner from Jerusalem into the hands of the Romans.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>When they had examined me, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27903T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27903T\"></sup>wished to set me at liberty, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27903U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27903U\"></sup>because there was no reason for the death penalty in my case.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But because the Jews objected, I was compelled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27904V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27904V\"></sup>to appeal to Caesar—though I had no charge to bring against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27904W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27904W\"></sup>my nation.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For this reason, therefore, I have asked to see you and speak with you, since it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27905X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27905X\"></sup>because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27905Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27905Y\"></sup>the hope of Israel that I am wearing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27905Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27905Z\"></sup>this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27905AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27905AA\"></sup>chain.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And they said to him, “We have received no letters from Judea about you, and none of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27906AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27906AB\"></sup>the brothers coming here has reported or spoken any evil about you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But we desire to hear from you what your views are, for with regard to this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27907AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27907AC\"></sup>sect we know that everywhere <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27907AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27907AD\"></sup>it is spoken against.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When they had appointed a day for him, they came to him at his lodging in greater numbers. From morning till evening <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27908AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27908AE\"></sup>he expounded to them, testifying to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27908AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27908AF\"></sup>the kingdom of God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27908AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27908AG\"></sup>trying to convince them about Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27908AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27908AH\"></sup>both from the Law of Moses and from the Prophets.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27909AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27909AI\"></sup>some were convinced by what he said, but others disbelieved.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And disagreeing among themselves, they departed after Paul had made one statement: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27910AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27910AJ\"></sup>“The Holy Spirit was right in saying to your fathers through Isaiah the prophet:",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27911AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27911AK\"></sup>“‘Go to this people, and say,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27911AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27911AL\"></sup>“You will indeed hear but never understand,and you will indeed see but never perceive.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27912AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27912AM\"></sup>For this people's heart has grown dull,and with their ears they can barely hear,and their eyes they have closed;lest they should see with their eyesand hear with their earsand understand with their heartand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27912AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27912AN\"></sup>turn, and I would heal them.’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore let it be known to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27913AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27913AO\"></sup>this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27913AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27913AP\"></sup>salvation of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27913AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27913AQ\"></sup>has been sent to the Gentiles; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27913AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27913AR\"></sup>they will listen.”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>He lived there two whole years at his own expense, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27914AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27914AS\"></sup>welcomed all who came to him,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27915AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27915AT\"></sup>proclaiming <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27915AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27915AU\"></sup>the kingdom of God and teaching about the Lord Jesus Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27915AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27915AV\"></sup>with all boldness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-27915AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-27915AW\"></sup>without hindrance."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;